EMy%20name%20helps%20me%20stand%20out%20at%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20works%20in%20the%20congressional%20advocacy%20space%2C%20where%20I%20help%20advocate%20for%20things%20like%20better%20wages%2C%20pay%20benefits%2C%20and%20technology%2C%20it%20helps%20to%20have%20a%20name%20like%20mine%20because%20people%20usually%20remember%20it.%20When%20I%20introduce%20myself%20to%20new%20staffers%2C%20new%20constituents%2C%20new%20lawmakers%2C%20or%20interns%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-be-more-memorable-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey'll%20remember%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20weeks%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20months%20later.%20That's%20a%20good%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20in%20my%20line%20of%20work%20you%20meet%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%20At%20some%20point%2C%20it%20feels%20very%20transactional.%20So%2C%20it's%20good%20to%20have%20something%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-job-tips-first-3-months-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelps%20you%20stand%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20my%20name.%20When%20people%20remember%20my%20name%20they%20also%20remember%20the%20ball%20I'm%20trying%20to%20push%20forward%2C%20and%20that's%20what's%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20use%20my%20name%20to%20make%20conversations%20more%20light-hearted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20work%2C%20we%20host%20an%20event%20where%20we%20onboard%20our%20congressional%20interns%20in%20Congress.%20With%20this%20event%2C%20our%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20reduce%20their%20anxiety%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20networking%2C%20and%20we%20try%20to%20show%20them%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-white-house-intern-day-in-the-life-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20as%20interns%3C%2Fa%3E%20truly%20matters.%20At%20the%20event%2C%20when%20my%20name%20comes%20up%2