e%20I'm%20serious%20about%20the%20work%20we're%20doing.%20I%20very%20much%20take%20pride%20in%20the%20work%20that%20we%20do%2C%20and%20after%20a%20minute%2C%20or%20two%2C%20people%20see%20how%20dedicated%20I%20am%20to%20the%20cause%20we're%20working%20on%20and%20my%20name%20doesn't%20take%20away%20from%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20use%20my%20middle%20initial%20to%20help%20avoid%20confusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20do%20interviews%20with%20the%20press%2C%20I%20ask%20them%20to%20please%20quote%20me%20as%20Taylor%20J.%20Swift%2C%20so%20no%20one%20confuses%20me%20as%20the%20pop%20singer.%20This%20way%2C%20no%20one%20wonders%20why%20Taylor%20Swift%20(without%20the%20J)%20is%20speaking%20on%20congressional%20modernization%20and%20oversight.%20I%20also%20include%20the%20%26quot%3BJ%26quot%3B%20on%20my%20business%20cards%20or%20when%20applying%20to%20jobs%2C%20to%20avoid%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20still%2C%20people%20do%20wonder.%20For%20example%2C%20just%20this%20past%20weekend%2C%20I%20booked%20a%20dinner%20reservation%20for%20two%20under%20the%20name%20Taylor%20Swift.%20I%20could%20tell%20the%20hostess%20seemed%20a%20bit%20disappointed%20when%20I%20showed%20up.%20Like%20normal%2C%20they%20joked%20about%20how%20I%20wasn't%20the%20real%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20so%20I%20just%20laughed%20and%20said%2C%20I%20hear%20it%20all%20the%20time%20but%20I%20just%20%3Cem%3Eshake%20it%20off%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20think%2C%20that%20if%20my%20name%20is%20the%20biggest%20struggle%20I%20have%20in%20life%2C%20I'm%20doing%20OK.%20It%20feels%20trivial%20to%20believe%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20your%20name%20has%20an%20effect%20on%20your%20career%20or%20job%20and%20you%20want%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20please%20email%20Manseen%20Logan%20at%20mlogan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhaving-name-taylor-swift-has-