he%20Miss%20World%202023%2C%20marking%20the%20return%20of%20the%20prestigious%20international%20beauty%20pageant%20to%20the%20country%20after%20a%20hiatus%20of%2028%20years.%20The%2071st%20edition%20of%20Miss%20World%20is%20anticipated%20to%20take%20place%20in%20November%2C%20with%20the%20final%20dates%20yet%20to%20be%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20India%20hosted%20the%20Miss%20World%20pageant%20was%20in%201996%2C%20making%20it%2028%20years%20since%20the%20nation%20showcased%20its%20hospitality%20and%20cultural%20richness%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESini%20Shetty%2C%20crowned%20the%20winner%20of%20the%20Femina%20Miss%20India%202022%20title%2C%20will%20be%20representing%20India%20at%20the%20upcoming%20Miss%20World%202023%20pageant.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20opportunity%2C%20Shetty%20expressed%20her%20enthusiasm%20for%20showcasing%20India's%20diverse%20traditions%20and%20values%20to%20her%20fellow%20contestants%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20then%2C%20we%20used%20to%20call%20India%20as%20a%20land%20of%20snake%20charmers.%20There%20is%20a%20small%20tweak%2C%20we%20are%20still%20charmers%20and%20have%20charmed%20everyone.%20And%20I%20hope%20everyone%20coming%20here%20is%20charmed%20by%20our%20traditions%2C%20our%20hospitality%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Shetty%20said%20during%20an%20exclusive%20conversation%20with%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20enduring%20relevance%20of%20the%20Miss%20World%20pageant%2C%20she%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BMiss%20World%20pageant%20hasn't%20lost%20its%20relevance%20yet.%20A%20group%20of%20women%20coming%20together%20and%20standing%20up%20for%20issues%20they%20believe%20in.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20say%20beauty%20with%20a%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shetty%20emphasized%20the%20unique%20blend%20of%20modernity%20and%20tradition%20that%20defines%20India%2C%20describing%20the%20country%20as%20a%20living%20monument.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20an%20amalgamation%20of%20what%20a%20modern%20world%20and%20a%20traditional%20world%20looks%20like.%20Participants%20coming%20here%20for%20the%20pageant%20will%20be%20wowed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20young%20individuals%20in%20the%20era%20of%20social%20media%2C%20Ms%20Shetty%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20self-acceptance.%20%26quot%3BConfidence%20is%20something%20that%20comes%20when%20you%20talk%20to%20yourself%20in%20the%20mirror%20and%20say%20that%20you%20are%20perfect%20the%20way%20you%20are.%20Social%20media%20has%20put%20up%20an%20image%2C%20and%20the%20reel%20life%20has%20taken%20over.%20So%20kids%20today%20do%20doubt%20about%20themselves.%20They%20should%20just%20feel%20comfortable%20in%20their%20own%20skin%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20encouraged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20concluding%20statement%2C%20Ms%20Shetty%20highlighted%20the%20deeper%20purpose%20behind%20the%20beauty%20pageant.%20%26quot%3BBeauty%20comes%20as%20part%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20but%20the%20purpose%20is%20much%20bigger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20eagerly%20awaits%20the%20Miss%20World%202023%2C%20it%20is%20poised%20to%20present%20not%20only%20the%20beauty%20of%20its%20contestants%20but%20also%20the%20rich%20tapestry%20of%20its%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20the%20strength%20of%20purpose%20that%20defines%20the%20Miss%20World%20pageant.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708077840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ft4peluq_sini-shetty-_650x400_16_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-snake-charmers-to-charming-world-sini-shetty-on-india-hosting-miss-world-5069164%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20momentous%20announcement%2C%20India%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20host%20the%20Miss%20World%202023%2C%20marking%20the%20return%20of%20the%20prestigious%20international%20beauty%20pageant%20to%20the%20country%20after%20a%20hiatus%20of%202