%20started%20selling%20embroidered%20products%20on%20her%20Etsy%20shop%20at%2017%20but%20orders%20dried%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConsistently%20posting%20on%20TikTok%20and%20customization%20led%20to%20her%20business%20finally%20taking%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Keida%20Dervishi%2C%20the%2021-year-old%20founder%20of%20Soulmate%20Customs.%20The%20revenue%20has%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20young%20girl%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20I'd%20follow%20in%20my%20parents'%20footsteps.%20They%20moved%20from%20Albania%20to%20the%20US%20before%20I%20was%20born%20and%20owned%20a%20fashion%20line.%20I%20grew%20up%20traveling%20to%20trade%20shows%20all%20over%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20always%20curious%20about%20my%20parents'%20businesses%2C%20but%20my%20passion%20was%20singing%20and%20acting.%20As%20a%20nine-year-old%2C%20I%20competed%20in%20Gjeniu%20I%20Vogel%2C%20a%20televised%20Albanian%20children's%20singing%20competition.%20As%20a%20teenager%2C%20I%20appeared%20in%20TV%20shows%20and%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BFresh%20Off%20the%20Boat%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wrong%20Husband%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Council.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20time%20to%20try%20something%20new.%20At%20age%2017%2C%20I%20saw%20other%20teenagers%20on%20TikTok%20starting%20businesses.%20I%20purchased%20a%20%24300%20embroidery%20machine%20with%20my%20parents'%20help.%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20a%20side%20hobby%20to%20earn%20some%20income.%20I%20didn't%20expect%20it%20to%20blow%20up.%20Soulmate%20Customs%20made%20over%20%241%20million%20in%20sales%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20hasn't%20always%20been%20easy.%20There%20have%20been%20some%20failures%20in%20growth%20that%20were%20our%20fault.%20But%20even%20with%20failures%2C%20we've%20learned%20from%20our%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20had%20some%20early%20success%20thanks%20to%20TikTok%2C%20but%20sales%20dried%20up%20fast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20machine%20in%20December%202020%2C%20six%20months%20after%20graduating%20from%20high%20school.%20I%20unpacked%20it%2C%20opened%20up%20YouTube%2C%20and%20searched%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20embroider%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20use%20it%20in%20a%20day.%20After%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20I%20felt%20confident%20enough%20to%20start%20selling%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20an%20Etsy%20embroidery%20shop%20before%20founding%20Soulmate%20Customs.%20Using%20an%20app%20called%20Procreate%2C%20I%20drew%20designs%20on%20my%20old%20iPad.%20Once%20I%20had%20a%20design%20I%20liked%2C%20I'd%20put%20it%20on%20a%20USB%20and%20plug%20it%20into%20the%20machine%2C%20which%20automatically%20digitized%20the%20design%20to%20embroider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20a%20few%20orders%20initially%2C%20but%20things%20boomed%20when%20I%20posted%20a%20design%20inspired%20by%20Olivia%20Rodrigo's%20song%20Driver's%20License%20on%20TikTok.%20The%20video%20got%20around%204%20million%20views%2C%20and%20my%20shop%20had%20over%20300%20orders%20in%20three%20months.%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20made%20it!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20song's%20hype%20died%20down%20in%202021%2C%20the%20orders%20dried%20up%20on%20my%20Etsy%20shop%2C%20and%20I%20freaked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20birthday%20gift%20for%20my%20mom%20was%20the%20spark%20for%20Soulmate%20Customs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20time%20orders%20dwindled%2C%20my%20mom's%20birthday%20was%20coming%20up.%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20I%20take%20a%20picture%20of%20me%20and%20her%2C%20outline%20it%2C%20and%20embroider%20it%20with%20the%20embroidery%20machine%20I%20already%20have%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20mom%20opened%20the%20shirt%20with%20the%20embroidered%20outline%20of%20us%2C%20she%20started%20crying.%20She%20told%20me%20it%20would%20be%20a%20great%20idea%20for%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20year%2C%20in%20July%202021%2C%20we%20launched%20Soulmate%20Customs%2C%20which%20makes%20soulmate-themed%20custom%20embroidery%20clothing.%20My%20mom%20is%20a%20cofounder%20because%20she%20is%20very%20involved%20in%20the%20business%20and%20helped%20set%20up%20all%20the%20legal%20paperwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22986%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20young%20woman%20sits%20at%20a%20desk%2C%20mother%20stand%20behind%20her.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cdeec86fcb546d2d500418%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221118%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKeida%20Dervishi%20and%20her%20mom%2C%20who%20is%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Soulmate%20Customs%3Cp%3EKeida%20Dervishi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20got%20our%20first%20order%20after%204%20days%20and%20made%20our%20first%20%24100%2C000%20in%204%20weeks%2C%20thanks%20to%20TikTok%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20experiencing%20the%20drastic%20fall%20in%20orders%20with%20my%20first%20Esty%20shop%2C%20I%20knew%20for%20Soulmate%20Customs%2C%20I%20had%20to%20be%20promoting%20it%20on%20TikTok%20constantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20vlog-style%20content%20of%20me%20embroidering.%20After%20about%20four%20days%20of%20posting%2C%20we%20got%20our%20first%20order.%20I%20did%20a%20mini-vlog%20of%20making%20and%20shipping%20that%20first%20order.%20About%2030%20minutes%20after%20posting%20the%20TikTok%2C%20we%20saw%20floods%20of%20new%20followers%20and%20supportive%20comments.%20The%20video%20was%20blowing%20up.%20It%20ended%20up%20getting%203.7%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20hearing%20the%20sale%20%26quot%3Bcha-ching%26quot%3B%20on%20my%20phone%20repeatedly.%20I%20was%20sitting%20with%20my%20mom%20on%20the%20couch%2C%20and%20we%20looked%20at%20each%20other%20in%20shock.%20We%20got%20over%201%2C400%20orders%20in%20the%20first%20month%20and%20made%20over%20%24100%2C000%20in%20sales.%20It%20was%20a%20huge%20jump-start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20business%20became%20a%20family%20affair%20immediately%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20those%20orders%20came%20in%2C%20the%20business%20was%20still%20one%20%24300%20embroidery%20machine%20in%20my%20parents'%20house.%20There%20was%20no%20way%20that%20I%20could%20fulfill%20every%20single%20order%20on%20time.%20I%20told%20my%20mom%20we'd%20have%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20said%20we%20weren't%20shutting%20down.%20She%20sent%20my%20dad%20to%20look%20for%20office%20space.%20We%20rented%20out%20the%20second%20office%20we%20saw%20and%20have%20moved%20twice%20since%20then.%20We%20invested%20in%20four%20commercial%20embroidery%20machines%20and%20hired%20anyone%20we%20could%20find%20just%20to%20help%20us%20fulfill%20all%20of%20the%20orders.%20Thankfully%2C%20we%20did%20it%20successfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20became%20a%20family%20affair.%20My%20mom%20runs%20the%20entire%20production%20and%20back-end%20parts%20of%20the%20business.%20We%20call%20her%20the%20%26quot%3BKris%20Jenner%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dad%20deals%20with%20the%20operations.%20He%20fixes%20machines%2C%20buys%20new%20machines%20we%20need%2C%20and%20trains%20staff.%20My%20older%20brother%20Kenny%20handles%20everything%20marketing%20%E2%80%94%20running%20ads%2C%20email%2C%20and%20SMS%20campaigns.%20A%20big%20part%20of%20his%20work%20is%20also%20accounting.%20We%20are%20fully%20family-owned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPosting%20constantly%20means%20momentum%20doesn't%20fizzle%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20from%20my%20Olivia%20Rodrigo%20success%20that%20after%20a%20business%20blows%20up%20on%20social%20media%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20keep%20the%20fire%20going.%20So%2C%20I%20knew%20creating%20a%20lot%20of%20content%20would%20be%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20get%20into%20the%20office%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20do%20is%20post%20a%20video.%20I%20post%20five%20to%20eight%20times%20per%20day%20on%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram.%20It's%20the%20most%20important%20part%20of%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20with%20trending%20sounds%20and%20video%20formats.%20I%20see%20what's%20going%20viral%20and%20copy%20the%20trend.%20Drama%20also%20sells.%20For%20example%2C%20I've%20made%20so%20many%20drama%20videos%20where%20I%20include%20customers%20who%20reach%20out%20to%20us%20with%20their%20stories.%20In%20one%20video%2C%20a%20customer%20reached%20out%20to%20us%20saying%20that%20one%20of%20the%20custom%20orders%20she%20saw%20on%20our%20page%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40soulmatecustoms%2Fvideo%2F7171546373848861994%3F_r%3D1%26_t%3D8iBNGq3TxSl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20boyfriend%20ordering%20for%20another%20girl%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPosting%20a%20lot%20content%20on%20TikTok%20has%20been%20key%20to%20keeping%20our%20business%20thriving.%20We%20hit%20%241%20million%20in%20revenue%20in%202022%20in%20just%2011%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERelying%20on%20virality%20is%20tough%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20huge%20ups%20and%20downs%20because%20we%20rely%20on%20virality%2C%20which%20can%20be%20tough.%20Views%20aren't%20consistent%2C%20so%20I'm%20looking%20for%20more%20stable%20ways%20to%20grow%20the%20business%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20we%20can%20keep%20on%20scaling%20at%20all%20periods%20of%20the%20year%2C%20not%20just%20whenever%20we%20go%20viral%20or%20during%20seasonal%20peaks.%20Valentine's%20Day%2C%20Mother's%20Day%2C%20and%20Father's%20day%20are%20when%20we%20see%20a%20bump%20in%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAs%20a%20young%20founder%2C%20I%20haven't%20always%20made%20the%20right%20calls%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20hit%20%241%20million%2C%20we%20had%20a%20super%20small%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20mistakes%20that%20I%20made%20in%20growing%20the%20business%20last%20year%20was%20over-hiring.%20Because%20we%20grew%20so%20quickly%20initially%2C%20I%20thought%20more%20team%20members%20would%20help%20us%20keep%20growing.%20We%20hired%20graphic%20designers%2C%20extra%20content%20creators%2C%20and%20videographers.%20I%20overhired%2C%20and%20it%20got%20very%20costly%20very%20quickly.%20It%20was%20a%20big%20lesson.%20Now%2C%20we've%20found%20a%20better%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20women%20smiling%20in%20a%20workshops%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cdef056fcb546d2d500425%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22858%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKeida%20Dervishi%20with%20the%20Soulmate%20Customs%20team.%3Cp%3EKeida%20Dervishi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20focus%20is%20on%20growing%20the%20business%20rather%20than%20college%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchool%20has%20never%20been%20a%20huge%20priority%20to%20me.%20My%20parents%20didn't%20push%20me%20to%20go%20to%20college.%20When%20I%20would%20have%20applied%20for%20college%2C%20the%20business%20took%20off%20and%20sent%20my%20life%20in%20a%20different%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20start%20the%20business%20with%20this%20endgame%20in%20mind.%20Now%20that%20we're%20at%20seven%20figures%2C%20I'm%20fighting%20with%20everything%20I%20can%20to%20keep%20it%20going.%20It's%20been%20very%20stressful.%20There%20have%20been%20times%20when%20I've%20been%20so%20overwhelmed%20that%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20can%20keep%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReaching%20out%20to%20other%20people%20on%20social%20media%20has%20helped%20a%20lot.%20Instagram%20has%20been%20a%20big%20platform%20for%20me%20to%20make%20connections%20with%20business%20people%20and%20others%20who%20are%20doing%20cool%20things%20with%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturned-esty-side-hustle-into-million-dollar-business-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusines