0in%20the%20rows%20directly%20right%20of%20me%20and%20diagonal%20me%20were%20broken%20as%20well.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce3181f533b039a883f5c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TVs%20in%20the%20rows%20directly%20right%20of%20me%20and%20diagonal%20to%20me%20were%20also%20broken%2C%20though%20those%20were%20stuck%20on%20a%20white%20screen.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20realized%20my%20TV%20was%20broken%2C%20I%20walked%20through%20the%20cabin%20to%20see%20how%20many%20others%20were%20out.%20I%20counted%20at%20least%2015%20screens%20stuck%20on%20a%20white%20loading%20page%2C%20including%20the%20person%20directly%20across%20from%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20told%20me%20that%20affected%20passengers%20could%20reach%20out%20to%20Air%20India%20after%20the%20flight%20to%20request%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlso%20broken%20was%20the%20USB%20port%2C%20meaning%20I%20then%20had%20to%20be%20conservative%20with%20my%20battery%20when%20watching%20my%20pre-downloaded%20movies%20and%20shows.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20broken%20USB%20port.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce31e0a610a9069d593ca1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20broken%20USB%20port.%20There%20wasn't%20an%20outlet%20under%20the%20seat%2C%20either.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20there%20was%20a%20chance%20my%20television%20could%20fail%2C%20I%20downloaded%20enough%20content%20to%20keep%20me%20entertained%20for%20days.%20This%20mostly%20included%20podcasts%20and%20bingeable%20TV%20shows%20like%20Survivor%20and%20NCIS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20portable%20charger%20was%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20already%20more%20than%20half-dead%20by%20the%20time%20I%20boarded%2C%20so%20I%20was%20careful%20with%20my%20aging%20iPhone's%20battery%20life%20when%20watching%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20had%20to%20save%20battery%20for%20things%20like%20podcasts%20and%20Spotify%20when%20trying%20to%20sleep%20%E2%80%94%20I%20can't%20just%20listen%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20the%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20a%20backup%20to%20the%20backup%2C%20I%20brought%20a%20book%20just%20in%20case%20I%20found%20myself%20without%20any%20entertainment%20at%20all.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Book%20of%20Lost%20and%20Found.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce3206f533b039a883f5fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20brought%20%26quot%3BThe%20Book%20of%20Lost%20and%20Found%26quot%3B%20by%20Lucy%20Foley.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20was%20particularly%20helpful%20when%20my%20phone%20was%20out%20of%20reach%20charging%20at%20another%20passenger's%20seat%2C%20who%20was%20nice%20enough%20to%20let%20me%20use%20their%20USB%20when%20they%20weren't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EReading%20wasn't%20entirely%20easy%2C%20though.%20My%20remote%20not%20only%20didn't%20signal%20to%20the%20TV%2C%20but%20it%20also%20wouldn't%20turn%20on%20my%20reading%20light.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20trying%20to%20use%20the%20remote.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce322da610a9069d593cb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENothing%20responded%20to%20the%20remote%2C%20so%20it%20was%20useless%20on%20the%20flight.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20external%20button%20on%20the%20ceiling%20for%20a%20reading%20light%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20my%20phone's%20screen.%20I%20propped%20the%20phone%20against%20my%20chest%2C%20facing%20the%20book%2C%20and%20maxed%20out%20the%20brightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20perfect%2C%20but%20it%20worked%20well%20enough%2C%20and%20I%20could%20see%20the%20pages%20without%20getting%20a%20headache%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20yet%20another%20thing%20that%20killed%20my%20phone%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20between%20balancing%20a%20light%20to%20read%20and%20keeping%20my%20phone%20charged%2C%20I%20mostly%20slept%20thanks%20to%20melatonin.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cabin%20lighting%20was%20pink%20and%20blue.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce3288f533b039a883f630%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cabin%20lighting%20helped%20me%20sleep%2C%20too.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20kill%20between%20Delhi%20and%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20sleep%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20to%20avoid%20boredom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%2015%20hours%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20sleep%20for%20about%20six%20in%20between%20meals%2C%20reading%2C%20and%20watching%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20the%20key%20amenities%20expected%20to%20work%20on%20an%20ultra-long-haul%20flight%20were%20busted%2C%20the%20aging%20seat%20wasn't%20all%20bad.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20overhead%20bins%20with%20luggage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce33426fcb546d2d501915%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20didn't%20struggle%20to%20find%20space%20for%20my%20carry-on%20luggage.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20amenities%20I%20rely%20on%20for%20entertainment%20%E2%80%94%20the%