f%20fraudulent%20marriages%20involving%20Non-Resident%20Indians%20(NRIs)%20marrying%20Indian%20partners%20is%20a%20worrisome%20trend.%20Several%20reports%20highlight%20an%20increasing%20pattern%20where%20these%20marriages%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20deceptive%2C%20putting%20Indian%20spouses%2C%20especially%20women%2C%20in%20precarious%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Awasthi%20said%20in%20his%20covering%20letter%20to%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20legislation%2C%20the%20panel%20said%2C%20should%20be%20made%20applicable%20not%20only%20to%20the%20NRIs%20but%20also%20to%20those%20individuals%20who%20come%20within%20the%20definition%20of%20'Overseas%20Citizens%20of%20India'%20(OCIs)%20as%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%201955.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20further%20recommended%20that%20all%20marriages%20between%20the%20NRIs%2FOCIs%20and%20Indian%20citizens%20should%20be%20made%20compulsorily%20registered%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Awasthi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20comprehensive%20central%20legislation%20should%20also%20include%20provisions%20on%20divorce%2C%20maintenance%20of%20spouse%2C%20custody%20and%20maintenance%20of%20children%2C%20serving%20of%20summons%2C%20warrants%2C%20or%20judicial%20documents%20on%20the%20NRIs%20and%20OCIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20it%20is%20recommended%20that%20requisite%20amendments%20need%20to%20be%20introduced%20in%20the%20Passports%20Act%2C%201967%20in%20order%20to%20mandate%20the%20declaration%20of%20marital%20status%2C%20the%20linking%20of%20a%20spouse's%20passport%20with%20the%20other%20and%20mentioning%20of%20the%20marriage%20registration%20number%20on%20the%20passports%20of%20both%20the%20spouses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20recalled%20that%20in%20order%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20emerging%20situation%2C%20the%20Registration%20of%20Marriage%20of%20Non-Resident%20Indians%20Bill%2C%202019%2C%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20February%2011%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%2016th%20(previous)%20Lok%20Sabha%20referred%20the%20bill%20to%20the%20Committee%20on%20External%20Affairs.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20same%20bill%20was%20again%20referred%20to%20the%20Committee%20on%20External%20Affairs%20after%20the%2017th%20(present)%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20constituted%2C%20for%20further%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20deliberations%20continued%2C%20the%20Law%20Commission%20received%20a%20reference%20on%20the%20NRI%20Bill%2C%202019%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20conveyed%20through%20the%20Law%20Ministry%20in%20April%20last.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708076580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-02%2Fwedding-generic_650x400_51486039187.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-law-panel-said-about-worrisome-trend-in-nris-ocis-marrying-indians-5068882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Describing%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bworrisome%20trend%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3Brising%26quot%3B%20cases%20of%20fraudulent%20marriages%20between%20NRIs%20and%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20the%20Law%20Commission%20has%20recommended%20a%20comprehensive%20law%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20situation%20and%20compulsory%20registration%20of%20such%20alliances.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-law-panel-said-about-worrisome-trend-in-nris-ocis-marrying-indians-5068882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-law-panel-said-about-worrisome-trend-in-nris-ocis-marrying-indians-506888