3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haldwani%20Muslims%20Fear%20Death%20Toll%20Maybe%20Higher%20Than%20Official%20Figures%3A%20Fact-Finding%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F06124211%2FPHOTO-2023-01-04-20-52-47.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20violence%20which%20erupted%20in%20Gafoor%20Basti%2C%20Haldwani%20on%20February%208%20over%20the%20demolition%20of%20a%20mosque%20and%20madrasa%20built%20on%20government%20land%2C%20the%20police%20searched%20approximately%20300%20homes%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwatch-haldwani-unrest-violence-arrests-and-unanswered-questions%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20beatings%2C%20detentions%20and%20property%20damages%20and%20internet%20shutdown%20in%20the%20area%20aggravated%20the%20fear%20of%20the%20locals%20and%20they%20feel%20that%20the%20actual%20death%20toll%20may%20be%20higher%20than%20the%20official%20figures%2C%20a%20seven-member%20fact%20finding%20team%20wrote%20in%20a%20report%20on%20the%20Haldwani%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficially%2C%20six%20people%20were%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2024%2F02%2F09%2Fdel106-ldall-uttarakhand.html%5C%22%3E%20reportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20killed%20in%20the%20clashes.%20The%20incident%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Coutcome%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnarrative%E2%80%9D%20built%20by%20Uttarakhand%20Chief%20Minster%20Pushkar%20Dhami%20and%20radical%20right-wing%20citizen%20groups%20to%20%3Cspan%3Ecreate%20the%20northern%20state%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20%3Cem%3EDevbhoomi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20holy%20land%20for%20Hindus%2C%20which%20would%20have%20no%20place%20for%20other%20religious%20minorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20citizen%20fact%20finding%20report%20by%20Association%20for%20Protection%20of%20Civil%20Rights%20(APCR)%2C%20Karawan-e-Mohabbat%20and%20civil%20rights%20activist%20Zahid%20Qadri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esuggested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20underlined%20that%20there%20was%20a%20steady%20rise%20in%20communal%20tempers%20in%20Uttarakhand%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20which%20also%20resulted%20in%20calls%20for%20economic%20and%20social%20boycotts%20of%20Muslims%20and%20eviction%20of%20Muslim%20tenets%20from%20houses%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eshops%20and%20demands%20and%20threats%20for%20them%20to%20leave%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20the%20members%20of%20the%20fact%20finding%20team%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Haldwani%20incident%20was%20also%20a%20result%20of%20Dhami%E2%80%99s%20projection%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20destruction%20of%203000%20Mazaars%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20state%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Caccomplishment%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20government%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20silent%20on%20unauthorised%20Hindu%20religious%20structures%20in%20forest%20and%20Nazul%20lands%E2%80%9D%20(a%20type%20of%20government%20land%20used%20for%20non-agricultural%2C%20public%20purpose%20such%20as%20building%2C%20road%2C%20market%20and%20playground).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20finding%20team%20visited%20Haldwani%20on%20February%2014%20and%20prepared%20the%20interim%20report%20based%20on%20the%20conversations%20with%20civil%20society%20members%2C%20journalists%2C%20writers%20and%20lawyers%20and%20telephonic%20conversations%20with%20a%20few%20affected%20persons%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEviction%20stayed%20by%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20several%20disputes%20arose%20regarding%20the%20legal%20ownership%20of%20tracts%20of%20urban%20land%20in%20Muslim%20majority%20areas%20in%20Haldwani.%20While%20Muslims%20who%20occupy%20these%20lands%20claim%20to%20be%20the%20rightful%20lessees%2C%20the%20state%20government%20suggest%20that%20these%20are%20government%20lands%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20proposed%20eviction%20related%20to%C2%A0the%20claims%20by%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20regarding%20settlements%20in%20Railway%20land%20occupied%20by%20Muslim%20residents%20in%20Haldwani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bulldozers%20were%20out%20while%20matter%20was%20sub-judice%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20is%20related%20to%20around%20six%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20which%20a%2020-year-old%20mosque%20and%20a%20madrasa%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20masjid%20and%20madrasa%20were%20sealed%20by%20the%20local%20municipality%20on%20February%204%20after%20a%20group%20of%20ulemas%20met%20the%20municipality%20officials%20to%20plead%20against%20the%20eviction%20notices%20served%20on%20January%2030%20to%20vacate%20both%20the%20mosque%20and%20madrasa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20police%20asserted%20that%20the%20land%20belonged%20to%20the%20government%20while%20Sofiya%20Malik%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20the%20lessee%20of%20the%20disputed%20land%20approached%20the%20Uttarakhand%20High%20Court%20due%20to%20these%20recent%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20judge%20bench%20heard%20the%20matter%20on%20February%208%20and%20the%20next%20hearing%20was%20on%20February%2014.%20The%20local%20residents%20told%20the%20fact%20finding%20team%20that%20on%20February%208%20evening%20the%20local%20officers%20arrived%20with%20bulldozers%2C%20municipal%20workers%20and%20significant%20police%20protection%20to%20undertake%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20the%20madrasa%20%E2%80%9Cdespite%20the%20matter%20being%20sub-judice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-a-150-year-old-ploy-to-incite-religious-violence-is-still-used-in-india%5C%22%3EHow%20a%20150-Year-Old%20Ploy%20to%20Incite%20Religious%20Violence%20Is%20Still%20Used%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunity%20anger%20fuelled%20as%20women%20were%20beaten%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20fact%20finding%20report%2C%20a%20group%20of%20women%20residents%20who%20stood%20before%20the%20bulldozers%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20prevent%20the%20demolitions%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Futtarakhand-violence-erupts-in-haldwani-after-madrasa-demolition-shoot-at-sight-orders-issued%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20forcefully%20removed%2C%20dragged%20and%20beaten%20by%20male%20and%20female%20police%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20action%20angered%20the%20local%20community.%20Moreover%2C%20their%20plea%20that%20the%20Quran%20and%20other%20sacred%20properties%20in%20the%20mosque%20be%20respectfully%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eimam%3C%2Fem%3E%20before%20the%20demolition%20was%20also%20brushed%20aside%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20demolition%20began%20the%20local%20Muslims%20pelted%20stones%20and%20municipal%20workers%20and%20journalist%20who%20were%20present%20on%20the%20spot%20were%20injured.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20video%20evidence%20that%20highlights%20that%20the%20police%20also%20resorted%20to%20stone%20throwing%20on%20the%20crowd%2C%20the%20fact%20finding%20team%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPolice%20vehicles%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20the%20locals%3B%20violence%20escalated%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20underlined%20that%20the%20violence%20rapidly%20escalated%20as%20crowds%20set%20vehicles%20near%20the%20police%20station%20on%20fire%20which%20resulted%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20police%20station%20being%20ablaze.%20While%20the%20police%20responded%20with%20firing%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20when%20the%20firing%20started%20and%20when%20formal%20shoot-at-sight%20orders%20wer