20no%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20brother%20was%20standing%20next%20to%20me%20too.%20Aditya%20is%20a%20huge%20star%20and%20we%20love%20him%20that%20is%20why%20we%20went.%20He%20was%20taking%20selfies%20with%20everyone%20so%20I%20thought%20he%20would%20take%20with%20me%20too%20that's%20why%20I%20gave%20my%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Aditya%20Narayan%2C%20the%20student%20also%20mentioned%20during%20the%20interview%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20should%20have%20not%20done%20what%20he%20did%20to%20me%20even%20if%20it%20was%20some%20other%20student.%20We%20are%20all%20his%20fans%20and%20we%20love%20him%20a%20lot%20that%20is%20why%20we%20go%20to%20his%20concert.%20Hamare%20yaha%20kalakaro%20ki%20kami%20nahi%20hai%20vaise%20(We%20don't%20have%20dearth%20of%20artistes%20in%20our%20country).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsinger-aditya-narayans-reaction-after-bhilai-concert-video-goes-viral-i-am-answerable-to-the-almighty-5058834%5C%22%3EThe%20student's%20version%20lies%20in%20a%20sharp%20contradiction%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20what%20the%20concert's%20event%20manager%20earlier%20told%20Zoom.%20After%20the%20video%20went%20viral%20and%20Aditya%20was%20slammed%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Internet%2C%20the%20event%20manager%20issued%20a%20statement.%20He%20told%20Zoom%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20boy%20was%20not%20even%20a%20college%20student%2C%20he%20must%20be%20someone%20from%20outside%20the%20college.%20He%20was%20constantly%20dragging%20Aditya's%20feet%20nonstop.%20He%20was%20very%20irritating.%20He%20banged%20his%20phone%20on%20Aditya's%20feet%20multiple%20times.%20After%20that%20only%20did%20he%20lose%20his%20cool.%20He%20must%20have%20taken%20almost%20200%20selfies%20with%20this%20student.%20The%20whole%20concert%20went%20smooth%20apart%20from%20this.%20After%20this%20incident%2C%20the%20show%20went%20on%20for%20almost%20two%20hours.%20If%20the%20student%20was%20right%2C%20he%20would%20have%20come%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20manager%20added%20during%20his%20interaction%20with%20Zoom%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20Darshan%20Rawal%20stopped%20doing%20such%20college%20events%20because%20these%20kinds%20of%20activities%20keep%20happening%20in%20every%20city.%20People%20don't%20know%20the%20truth%20behind%20everything.%20You%20just%20see%20one%20side.%20He%20kept%20continuously%20hitting%20and%20dragging%20Aditya%2C%20what%20if%20he%20had%20fallen%20down%3F%20If%20this%20boy%20was%20right%2C%20he%20would%20have%20come%20forward%20and%20told%20the%20college%20authorities%20that%20this%20has%20happened%20to%20him.%20I%20have%20been%20connected%20with%20the%20college%20since%20many%20years%20and%20they%20haven't%20had%20a%20good%20concert%20like%20this%20one%20ever.%20They%20have%20said%20so%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20days%20ago%2C%20Aditya%20Narayan%20also%20reacted%20to%20the%20incident.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20Aditya%20Narayan%20told%20Times%20Now%2C%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20no%20comments.%20I%20am%20answerable%20to%20the%20Almighty.%20That's%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICYMI%2C%20This%20is%20the%20video%20we%20are%20talking%20about%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAditya%20Narayan%2C%20son%20of%20ace%20singer%20Udit%20Narayan%2C%20gained%20popularity%20through%20fans'%20support%2C%20but%20now%20he%20assaults%20a%20fan%20by%20throwing%20his%20mobile.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAdityaNarayan%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AdityaNarayan%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20be%20banned%20from%20participating%20in%20concerts%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20and%20apologize%20to%20the%20fan%20for%20his%20actions.%20He%20needs%20a%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fn2Chkx5FIr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F