img%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107750754.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERajeev%20Khandelwal%2C%20known%20for%20his%20role%20as%20Sujal%20in%20%26quot%3BKahin%20To%20Hoga%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20Karan%20Johar's%20OTT%20show%20%26quot%3BShowtime%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20he%20plays%20a%20superstar.%20He%20believes%20his%20character%20will%20remind%20people%20of%20various%20actors%2C%20reflecting%20the%20insecurities%20and%20beliefs%20of%20past%20superstars.%20The%20series%20also%20stars%20Emraan%20Hashmi%20and%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pacific%20Plate%20Being%20Torn%20Apart%20From%20Japan%20To%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Finds%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEarth's%20rigid%20outer%20shell%20is%20divided%20into%20a%20dozen%20large%20tectonic%20plates%2C%20and%20a%20major%20one%20-%20the%20Pacific%20plate%20-%20is%20being%20pulled%20apart.%20The%20discovery%20has%20been%20made%20by%20researchers%20from%20University%20of%20Toronto%20and%20is%20shedding%20new%20light%20on%20the%20century-old%20model%20of%20plate%20tectonics.%20The%20team%20found%20that%20the%20Pacific%20plate%20is%20scored%20by%20large%20undersea%20faults%20that%20are%20pulling%20it%20apart.%20The%20research%20has%20been%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fagupubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1029%2F2023GL105452%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGeophysical%20Research%20Letters%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20talks%20about%20the%20enormous%20forces%20that%20are%20tugging%20away%20the%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20undersea%20faults%20are%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%20long%20and%20thousands%20of%20metres%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20that%20geological%20deformations%20like%20faults%20happen%20on%20the%20continental%20plate%20interiors%20far%20from%20plate%20boundaries.%20But%20we%20didn't%20know%20the%20same%20thing%20was%20happening%20to%20ocean%20plates%2C%26quot%3B%20Erkan%20Gun%2C%20a%20post-doctoral%20researcher%20in%20the%20department%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20in%20the%20Faculty%20of%20Arts%20%26amp%3B%20Sciences%2C%20told%20phys.org.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20doing%20is%20refining%20plate%20tectonics-the%20theory%20that%20describes%20how%20our%20planet%20works-and%20showing%20those%20plates%20really%20aren't%20as%20pristine%20as%20we%20previously%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Russell%20Pysklywec%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20the%20department%20of%20Earth%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pacific%20plate%2C%20the%20largest%20tectonic%20plate%2C%20constitutes%20most%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20floor%2C%20stretching%20along%20the%20west%20coast%20of%20North%20America%20up%20to%20Alaska.%20At%20the%20western%20edge%2C%20it%20runs%20from%20Japan%20to%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20plate%20forms%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Ring%20of%20Fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20research%20has%20identified%20new%20points%20at%20which%20the%20Pacific%20plate%20is%20being%20pulled%20down%20into%20the%20mantle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20thought%20that%20because%20the%20sub-oceanic%20plateaus%20are%20thicker%2C%20they%20should%20be%20stronger.%20But%20our%20models%20and%20seismic%20data%20show%20it's%20actually%20the%20opposite%3A%20the%20plateaus%20are%20weaker%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%20studied%20four%20plateaus%20in%20the%20western%20Pacific%20Ocean%20-%20the%20Ontong%20Java%2C%20Shatsky%2C%20Hess%20and%20Manihiki%20-%20in%20a%20vast%20area%20roughly%20bounded%20by%20Hawaii%2C%20Japan%2C%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia.%20The%20data%20was%20then%20fed%20to%20a%20supercomputer%2C%20which%20compared%20it%20with%20information%20collected%20in%20studies%20done%20in%20the%201970s%20and%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20new%20finding%20like%20this%20overturns%20what%20we've%20understood%20and%20taught%20about%20the%20active%20Earth.%20And%20it%20shows%20that%20there%20are%20still%20radical%20mysteries%20about%20even%20the%20grand%20operation%20of%20our%20evolving%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pysklywec.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708075080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Frdbmaur_tectonic-plate-unsplash_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpacific-plate-being-torn-apart-from-japan-to-new-zealand-finds-study-5068889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20research%20has%20identified%20new%20points%20at%20which%20the%20Pacific%20plate%20is%20being%20pulled%20down%20into%20the%20mantle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpacific-plate-being-torn-apart-from-japan-to-new-zealand-finds-study-5068889%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpacific-plate-being-torn-apart-from-japan-to-new-zealand-finds-study-5068889%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpacific-plate-being-torn-apart-from-japan-to-new-zealand-finds-study-5068889%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Fresh%20Bout%20of%20Public%20Unrest%2C%20Arrests%20and%20Arson%3B%20Internet%20Suspended%20in%20Churachandpur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16145341%2FGGBKaMkWoAEYCW5.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Arson%2C%20arrests%20and%20public%20unrest%20continue%20to%20haunt%20Manipur%20as%20internet%20services%20have%20once%20again%20been%20snapped%20by%20the%20state%20government%20in%20the%20Kuki-majority%20Churachandpur%20after%20a%20mob%20attacked%20the%20superintenden