ting%20case%20of%205th%20IRBn%2C%20Chingarel%2C%20Imphal%20East%20by%20an%20unruly%20mob%20on%20the%20night%20of%2013.02.2024%2C%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20arrested%20six%20persons%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%20and%20they%20have%20been%20remanded%20to%20police%20custody%20by%20a%20judicial%20magistrate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFour%20Insas%20rifles%2C%20one%20AK%20Ghatak%2C%20two%20magazines%20of%20SLR%2C%20and%2016%20small%20boxes%20of%209mm%20ammunition%20looted%20from%20the%20IRBn%20camp%20have%20also%20been%20recovered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20PTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2024%2F02%2F16%2Fmanipur-6-arrested-for-looting-arms-from-irbn-camp%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20police%20did%20not%20mention%20from%20where%20the%20arms%20were%20recovered%2C%20or%20from%20where%20the%20persons%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20after%20the%20IRBn%20mob%20attack%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20l%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Earge%20number%E2%80%9D%20of%20village%20volunteers%20also%20attempted%20to%20barge%20into%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20Training%20College%20at%20Pangei%20in%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20located%20around%205%20kms%20from%20Chingarel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20state%20police%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20X%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20February%2013%2C%20in%20order%20to%20repel%20violent%20mobs%2C%20including%20armed%20miscreants%2C%20trying%20to%20storm%20MPTC%2C%20Pangei%2C%20security%20forces%20resorted%20to%20the%20use%20of%20legal%20force.%20During%20the%20incident%2C%20one%20person%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%20and%20three%20persons%20sustained%20injuries.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20also%20suspended%20seven%20IRBn%20personnel%20over%20the%20looting%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20from%20the%20camp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Commandant%20of%205th%20IRB%2C%20Chingarel%2C%20Imphal%20East%2C%20H.%20Balram%20Singh%20in%20an%20order%20said%20the%20seven%20personnel%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Csuspended%20with%20immediate%20effect%20and%20until%20further%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-mob-fury-in-churachandpur-after-cop-suspension%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20this%20move%20too%20was%20taken%20under%20Rule%2066%20of%20the%20Assam%20Police%20Manual%20Part-3%2C%20and%20that%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20may%20be%20initiated%20against%20them%20too%20for%20negligence%20and%20dereliction%20of%20duty.%20All%20suspended%20personnel%20have%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20not%20leave%20the%20camp%20without%20the%20prior%20permission%20of%20the%20station%20commandant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708074920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16145341%2FGGBKaMkWoAEYCW5.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-churachandpur-arrests-arson-unrest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attacks%20have%20seen%20large%20mobs%20barge%20into%20police%20stations%20or%20armouries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-churachandpur-arrests-arson-unrest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Riot%20Convict%20Extradited%20From%20UAE%20Within%204%20Months%20Of%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20most%20wanted%20criminal%20was%20extradited%20from%20the%20UAE%20on%20Friday%20after%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bgeo-located%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Gulf%20by%20Interpol%20channels.%20Narender%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20wanted%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20for%20murder%20and%20rioting%2C%20also%20faced%20a%20Red%20Corner%20Notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20convicted%20in%202009%20and%20jailed%20for%20life.%20Interpol%20had%20issued%20a%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20against%20him%20on%20November%207%20last%20year%20following%20a%20request%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Red%20notice%20was%20then%20circulated%20to%20all%20Interpol%20member%20countries%20to%20identify%20his%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20geo-located%20in%20the%20UAE%20through%20a%20close%20follow-up%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20via%20Interpol%2C%20the%20central%20agency%20said.%20Geo-locating%20someone%20means%20identifying%20the%20geographic%20location%20of%20an%20individual%20based%20on%20data%20collection%20mechanisms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI's%20Global%20Operations%20Centre%20coordinated%20with%20its%20National%20Central%20Bureau%20for%20Interpol%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20the%20Indian%20embassy%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20and%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20to%20secure%20his%20extradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Red%20Notice%20subject%20was%20returned%20today%20from%20UAE%20to%20India%20with%20a%20security%20detail%20from%20STF%20of%20Haryana%20Police%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20serves%20as%20the%20National%20Central%20Bureau%20for%20Interpol%20and%20coordinates%20with%20all%20local%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%20the%20country%20for%20assistance.%20The%20central%20agency%20issued%20around%20100%20Red%20Corner%20Notices%20in%202023%20and%20extradited%2029%20fugitives%20wanted%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708074900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F5s6hit8_narender-singh-_625x300_16_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Friot-convict-narender-singh-extradited-from-uae-within-4-months-of-red-corner-n