0huddled%20close%20to%20the%20frame%2C%20their%20tiny%20hands%20trying%20to%20light%20candles%20against%20the%20evening%20wind.%20It%20was%20six%20in%20the%20evening%20on%20December%2031%2C%20and%20the%20world%20was%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20welcoming%202024.%20Yet%2C%20time%20stood%20still%20inside%20the%20gates%20of%20the%20120-acre%20Prestige%20Lakeside%20Habitat%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%5C%22%3EBengaluru.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20three%20days%20before%20the%20memorial%2C%20Manya%2C%20like%20any%20other%20day%2C%20had%20gone%20to%20play%20with%20her%20friends%20around%20the%20swimming%20pool.%20What%20began%20as%20an%20ordinary%20playtime%20turned%20disastrous.%20Manya%20got%20electrocuted%20due%20to%20an%20unseen%20hazard%20in%20the%20pool%2C%20a%20dreadful%20incident%20that%20abruptly%20ended%20her%20young%20life%20and%20left%20her%20friends%20and%20the%20community%20in%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20did%20this%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCould%20it%20have%20been%20prevented%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%2C%20Rajesh%20Kumar%20Damerla%2C%20who%20had%20recently%20moved%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fprotests-over-proposed-10-storey-building-in-bengalurus-cubbon-park-5044287%5C%22%3EBengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shared%20his%20heartache%2C%20saying%2C%20'My%20daughter%20was%20a%20bright%20child%2C%20and%20we%20never%20thought%20this%20kind%20of%20incident%20would%20happen%20to%20her...She%20will%20never%20return%2C%20but%20I%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20parents%20anxious%20after%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%C2%A0told%C2%A0The%20Indian%20Express%C2%A0a%20day%20after%20the%20incident.%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Rajesh%20over%20text%2C%20but%20he's%20yet%20to%20respond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20RWA%20Dilemma%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20much%20anger%20has%20since%20been%20directed%20towards%20the%20elected%20RWA%20(Resident%20Welfare%20Association)%20leaders%2C%20let's%20face%20it-running%20these%20mini-cities%20cannot%20be%20a%20part-time%20job.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteer%20members%20of%20RWAs%20are%20often%20ill-equipped%20to%20handle%20the%20complexities%20of%20running%20what%20are%20essentially%20small%20towns.%20They%20are%20neighbours%2C%20not%20engineers%20or%20urban%20planners%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20safety%20and%20maintenance.%20Manya's%20tragedy%20painfully%20underscores%20the%20risk%20of%20entrusting%20critical%20community%20management%20to%20well-meaning%20but%20untrained%20volunteers.%20The%20arrest%20of%20seven%20individuals%2C%20including%20Debasish%20Sinha%2C%20the%20president%C2%A0of%20the%20RWA%2C%20has%20sent%20ripples%20of%20fear%20through%20the%20community.%20This%20fear%20isn't%20just%20about%20legal%20repercussions%3B%20it's%20about%20navigating%20the%20complexities%20of%20civic%20management%20without%20a%20safety%20net.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Residents%20pay%20their%20condolences%20to%20Manya%20Damerla%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Residents%20pay%20their%20condolences%20to%20Manya%20Damerla%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2bonl96o_manya-2_625x300_16_February_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20pay%20their%20condolences%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Pankaj%20Mishra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20tragedy%20that%20haunts%2C%20but%20the%20chilling%20realisation%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20shoulder%20responsibility%20in%20these%20unpredictable%20times.%20Debasish%2C%20a%20father%20of%20a%20two-year-old%20son%2C%20is%20currently%20locked%20in%20Bangalore%20Central%20Prison%2C%20Parappana%20Agrahara%2C%20around%2015%20kilometres%20from%20the%20society%20where%20his%20family%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat's%20concerning%20is%20that%20most%20of%20such%20sprawling%20complexes%20are%20run%20by%20volunteers.%20It's%20not%20about%20just%20one%20tragedy.%20It's%20about%20every%20resident%20living%20in%20a%20ticking%20time%20bomb.%20What%20becomes%20of%20those%20untrained%20volunteers%2C%20our%20neighbours%2C%20now%20thrust%20into%20roles%20demanding%20expertise%20they%20were%20never%20equipped%20with%3F%20Are%20they%20the%20scapegoats%20in%20a%20larger%20malaise%20of%20civic%20apathy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ENot%20An%20Isolated%20Incident%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Manya's%20death%2C%20the%20apartment's%20Telegram%20and%20WhatsApp%20groups%2C%20usually%20buzzing%20with%20mundane%20updates%20and%20greetings%2C%20transformed%20overnight.%20Residents%2C%20united%20in%20grief%20and%20disbelief%2C%20poured%20their%20emotions%20into%20messages%20that%20ranged%20from%20heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20venomous%20debates%20about%20what%20went%20wrong.%20It%20painted%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20community%20struggling%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20a%20senseless%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragedy%20shatters%20any%20illusion%20that%20we're%20cut%20off%20from%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fbengaluru-traffic-mess-can-it-be-solved-717961%5C%22%3E%20Bengaluru's%20broader%20troubles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20a%20harsh%20wake-up%20call%20to%20look%20beyond%20these%20walls%20and%20face%20the%20city's%20realities.%20These%20incidents%20aren't%20isolated%2C%20it's%20now%20becoming%20a%20pattern.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20Roshan%20Rasheed%2C%20a%2017-year-old%20student%2C%20met%20a%20tragic%20end%2C%20a%20fate%20eerily%20similar%20to%20Manya's.%20During%20a%20swimming%20competition%20at%20National%20Public%20School%20in%20the%20Agara%20area%2C%20Roshan%20collapsed%20and%20died%20just%20minutes%20after%20stepping%20out%20of%20the%20pool.%20It%20was%20a%20moment%20that%20stopped%20time%2C%20much%20like%20the%20incident%20at%20Prestige%20Lakeside%20Habitat.%20The%20police%2C%20after%20a%20year-long%20investigation%2C%20have%C2%A0recently%20confirmed%20what%20many%20feared%3A%20Roshan%20was%20electrocuted%20due%20to%20loose%20electrical%20wires%20lurking%20dangerously%20close%20to%20the%20pool.%20This%20revelation%2C%20detailed%20in%20a%20chargesheet%20based%20on%20forensic%20evidence%20and%20eyewitness%20accounts%2C%20shines%20a%20spotlight%20on%20negligence%20that's%20becoming%20all%20too%20familiar%20these%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EContrasting%20Realities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20gates%20of%20Prestige%2C%20the%20roads%20tell%20their%20own%20story.%20Potholes%20gape%20like%20open%20wounds.%20Accidents%20are%20frequent%20here%2C%20and%20heavy%20vehicles%20ply%20the%20roads%20without%20respite%2C%20indifferent%20to%20the%20delicate%20balance%20of%20residential%20life.%20The%20contrast%20was%20jarring%20-%20inside%2C%20everyone%20grappled%20with%20a%20tragic%20loss%20in%20a%20seemingly%20safe%20haven%2C%20while%20outside%2C%20life%20moved%20at%20a%20relentless%2C%20often%20reckless%2C%20pace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarthur%2C%20once%20just%20a%20fringe%20neighbourhood%20far%20from%20Bengaluru's%20urban%20dreams%2C%20now%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20city's%20unchecked%20growth.%20Home%20to%20IT%20giants%20and%20startups%20alike%2C%20the%20area%20throbs%20with%20the%20energy%20of%20innovation.%20But%20Varthur%20Lake%2C%20choked%20with%20the%20city's%20filth%2C%20is%20a%20mirror%20of%20the%20price%20of%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20pride%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20lakes%20now%20serve%20as%20sewage%20dumps%20or%20vanish%20under%20concrete%2C%20mirroring%20the%20city's%20crisis%20of%20prioritising%20growth%20over%20the%20green.%20Bengaluru%20has%20transformed%20into%20the%20heartland%20of%20India's%20technological%20revolution%20in%20the%20past%20thirty%20years.%20Its%20population%2C%20of%20roughly%20just%204%20million%20in%20the%20'90s%2C%20has%20grown%20to%20nearly%2013%20million%20today.%C2%A0%C2%A0This%20rapid%20urbanisation%20saw%20quaint%20villages%20such%20as%20Gunjur%20and%20Varthur%20evolve%20into%20bustling%20tech%20hubs.%20Meanwhile%2C%20once%20the%20city's%20lifeline%2C%20vital%20water%20bodies%20like%20lakes%20have%20been%20encroached%20upon%20for%20infrastructure%20developments%2C%20often%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20natural%20water%20channels%20feeding%20the%20remaining%20lakes.%20Out%20of%20nearly%202%2C000%20lakes%2C%20only%20about%20500%20are%20left%20now.%20While%20real%20estate%20developers%20gobble%20up%20all%20land%2C%20raising%20concrete%20jungles%20where%20trees%20once%20stood%2C%20the%20attention%20to%20infrastructural%20necessities%20within%20and%20without%20these%20luxurious%20compounds%20often%20remains%20woefully%20inadequate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gated%20society%20promised%20refuge%20from%20the%20world's%20dangers.%20Still%2C%20Manya's%20untimely%20death%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20no%20walls%20are%20high%20enough%20to%20keep%20out%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20city's%20mindless%20expansion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20Ripple%20Effect%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20community%20battled%20the%20tragedy%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20those%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20managing%20such%20residential%20societies.%20I%20spoke%20to%20Vishnu%20Gattupalli%2C%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Bangalore%20Apartments%20Federation%2C%20a%20body%20representing%20over%201%2C200%20RWAs.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThere%20needs%20to%20be%20focus%2C%20attention%2C%20and%20reflection%20on%20how%20to%20build%20and%20manage%20safety%20measures%20in%20semi-public%20spaces%20like%20apartment%20common%20areas%20and%20facilities%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishnu%20said.%20His%20perspective%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20broader%20implications%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20resonating%20with%20the%20fear%20and%20frustration%20of%20RWA%20members%20across%20the%20city.%20%26quot%3BThe%20arrest%20of%20the%20RWA%20president%20following%20this%20incident%20is%20also%20unfortunate%20and%20it%20has%20created%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20fear%20and%20uncertainty%20amongst%20thousands%20of%20RWAs%20across%20the%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishnu%20said%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20collective%20apprehension%20of%20those%20who%20volunteer%20their%20time%20for%20community%20welfare.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20now%20asking%20if%20we%20spend%20our%20precious%20time%20volunteering%2C%20can%20we%20still%20be%20jailed%20for%20such%20issues%3F%20Then%2C%20is%20it%20really%20worth%20it%3F%20It's%20a%20moral%20blow%20to%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20many%20RWA%20members%20across%20different%20communities%20have%20started%20resigning%20from%20their%20roles%2C%20rattled%20by%20the%20events%20at%20Prestige%20Lakeside.%20These%20exits%20will%20lead%20to%20indecision%20and%20anarchy%20in%20a%20gated%20community%20like%20Prestige%20Lakeside%2C%20with%20annual%20budgets%20of%20over%20Rs%2030%20crore%20and%20nearly%20300%20staff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20also%20highlighted%20the%20disparity%20in%20accountability%20and%20the%20perception%20of%20injustice%20within%20the%20system.%20%26quot%3BLast%20year%2C%20when%20a%20woman%20and%20her%20daughter%20got%20electrocuted%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20any%20news%20of%20the%20BESCOM%20MD%20getting%20arrested.%20Only%20the%20linemen%20were%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20RWA%20official%20pointed%20out.%20%26quot%3BRWA%20officials%20aren't%20criminals.%20And%20electricians%20and%20other%20maintenance%20staff%20aren't%20even%20directly%20employed%20by%20the%20RWA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EEchoes%20Of%20Neglect%3A%20Time%20To%20Act%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20remember%20Manya%2C%20a%20young%20life%20lost%20in%20a%20gated%20community%2C%20we%20can't%20forget%20other%20tragedies%20that%20mirror%20Bengaluru's%20broader%20problems.%20There's%20Roshan%20Rasheed%2C%20a%20young%20swimmer%2C%20who%20met%20his%20end%20through%20electrocution%20in%20a%20swimming%20pool%20during%20a%20competition%2C%20an%20incident%20similar%20to%20Manya's.%20And%20then%20there's%20the%20mother%20and%20daughter%2C%C2%A0Soundarya%20and%20her%20child%2C%20electrocuted%20by%20a%20live%20wire%20on%20Bengaluru's%20streets.%20Bengaluru%20is%20becoming%20a%20city%20racing%20mindlessly%20without%20pausing%20for%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20tragedies%2C%20happening%20in%20places%20as%20distinct%20as%20a%20school's%20swimming%20pool%20and%20a%20city%20street%2C%20show%20us%20that%20no%20place%20is%20immune%20in%20Bengaluru.%20They're%20not%20just%20names%20in%20the%20news%3B%20they're%20warnings%20of%20what%20happens%20when%20we%20overlook%20basic%20safety%20in%20our%20rush%20to%20build%20and%20expand.%20If%20we%20don't%20wake%20up%20now%2C%20we%20risk%20seeing%20these%20tragedies%20multiply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20responsibility%20that%20falls%20on%20all%20of%20them-%20policymakers%2C%20city%20planners%2C%20builders%2C%20RWA%20members%2C%20and%20every%20resident.%20Bengaluru%20needs%20to%20slow%20down%2C%20rethink%2C%20and%20rebuild%20with%20safety%20and%20sustainability%20at%20its%20core.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Pankaj%20Mishra%20has%20been%20a%20journalist%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20and%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20FactorDaily.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708074780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2bonl96o_manya-2_625x300_16_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-death-an-arrest-in-bengaluru-why-manyas-story-is-a-wake-up-call-5068121%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru's%20rapid%20urban%20growth%20has%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20shoddy%20civic%20planning%20and%20citizens'%20safety.%20The%20death%20of%20nine-year-old%20Manya%20in%20December%20is%20yet%20another%20reminder%20that%20the%20city%20needs%20immediate%20fixes.%2