ed%20his%20experience%20of%20working%20with%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%20and%20other%20top%20CEOs%2C%20including%20Meta's%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Microsoft's%20Satya%20Nadella.%20Mr%20Krishnan%20revealed%20this%20at%20a%20session%20titled%20'What%20did%20I%20learn%20from%20Elon%20and%20Zuckerberg'%20at%20the%20World%20Government%20Summit%20in%20UAE.%20The%20entrepreneur%20said%20that%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bworking%20class%20upbringing%26quot%3B%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20I%20taught%20myself%20to%20write%20code%20that%20led%20to%20a%20career%20in%20technology.%20I've%20been%20very%20fortunate%20and%20lucky.%20In%202007%2C%20I%20joined%20Microsoft.%20I%20worked%20for%20Satya%20for%20a%20bunch%20of%20years%20in%20Seattle%2C%20before%20he%20was%20the%20CEO%20of%20Microsoft.%20Then%20I%20was%20at%20Facebook%2C%20now%20Meta%2C%20working%20for%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%20Then%20I've%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20kind%20of%20work%20with%20Elon%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%20Most%20recently%2C%20or%20infamously%2C%20during%20the%20takeover%20at%20Twitter%20(X).%20Currently%2C%20I%20am%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Andreessen%20Horowitz.%20We%20are%20a%20large%20venture%20capital%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Krishnan%20told%20Time%20magazine's%20Executive%20Editor%20Naina%20Bajekal%20during%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20all%20successful%20CEOs%20have%20some%20common%20attributes.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20Zuckerberg%2C%20Elon%2C%20all%20these%20CEOs%2C%20they%20don't%20delegate%20as%20much%20as%20they're%20into%20the%20details.%20And%20if%20I%20could%20be%20provocative%2C%20I%20would%20say%20delegation%20is%20overrated%20and%20micromanagement%20is%20underrated.%20All%20the%20great%20CEOs%20I've%20met%20are%20always%20micromanagers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20with%20Mr%20Zuckerberg%2C%20the%20tech%20entrepreneur%20said%20that%20Meta%20CEO%20is%20a%20stickler%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20details.%20%26quot%3BYou%20would%20get%20a%20message%20from%20him%20in%20the%20morning%20about%20why%20is%20this%20number%20doing%20that.%20He%20would%20look%20at%20every%20single%20pixel.%20He%20would%20know%20things%20better%20than%20the%2022-year-old%20engineer%20who's%20working%20on%20it.%20This%20was%20in%202013.%20My%20wife%20worked%20at%20Meta%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%20and%20she%20was%20telling%20me%20that%20he%20is%20still%20the%20exact%20same%20way%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Krishnan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20mentioned%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20doesn't%20spend%20all%20his%20time%20sharing%20posts%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20there%20with%20him%2C%20when%20the%20Twitter%20acquisition%20happened%2C%2095%25%20of%20the%20meetings%20were%20with%20the%20junior%20most%20engineers.%20Like%20your%2025-year-old%20people.%20And%20he%20would%20be%20whiteboarding%20out%20diagrams%20and%20being%20in%20the%20details%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Krishnan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20how%20his%20life%20changed%20when%20he%20transitioned%20from%20Chennai%20to%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20Mr%20Krishnan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20very%20sort%20of%20traditional%20upbringing%20in%20India.%20I%20worked%20there%20for%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time%20in%20kind%20of%20a%20very%20traditional%20environment.%20And%20when%20I%20first%20went%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20it%20was%20honestly%20a%20huge%20culture%20shock%20because%20it%20operated%20so%20differently%20from%20where%20I%20had%20grown%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20whole%20interview%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FKBGf4Dpb4iM%3Fsi%3DgfvmOgN6WS6oZ02T%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Krishnan%20was%20born%20in%20Chennai%20and%20completed%20his%20BTech%20in%20Information%20Technology%20from%20SRM%20Engineering%20College%2C%20Anna%20University.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20United%20States%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021%20in%202005.%20His%20father%20worked%20in%20the%20insurance%20sector%2C%20while%20his%20mother%20was%20a%20homemaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20tech%20career%20started%20in%20Microsoft%20in%202005%2C%20where%20he%20mostly%20worked%20for%20the%20Windows%20Azure%20division.%20At%20Twitter%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20projects%20including%20its%20main%20timeline%2C%20building%20new%20UI%20for%20the%20platform%2C%20search%20and%20audience%20growth%20among%20others.%20He%20also%20developed%20mobile%20ad%20products%20At%20Facebook%20(now%20Meta)%20and%20Snap.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708070340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fa6b66kr_sriram-krishnan_625x300_01_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fif-you-look-at-elon-nadella-indian-techie-sriram-krishnan-on-working-with-top-ceos-5068492%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sriram%20was%20born%20in%20Chennai%20and%20completed%20his%20BTech%20in%20Information%20Technology%20from%20SRM%20Engineering%20College%2C%20Anna%20University.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fif-you-look-at-elon-nadella-indian-techie-sriram-krishnan-on-working-with-top-ceos-5068492%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fif-you-look-at-elon-nadella-indian-techie-sriram-krishnan-on-working-with-top-ceos-5068492%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fif-you-look-at-elon-nadella-indian-techie-sriram-krishnan-on-working-with-top-ceos-5068492%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kavit