0bank%20accounts%20and%20demanded%20Rs%20210%20crore%20as%20recovery%20over%20an%20alleged%2045-day%20delay%20in%20filing%20returns%20and%20cash%20contributions%20from%20its%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20press%20conference%20the%20party%20said%20that%20their%20accounts%20have%20been%20unfrozen.%20In%20a%20video%20message%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Vivek%20Tankha%20said%20that%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20un-froze%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20%E2%80%9Cpending%20further%20hearing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20treasurer%20Ajay%20%3C%2Fspan%3EMaken%20has%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20that%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20and%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20(ITAT)%20said%20in%20court%20that%20the%20party%20has%20to%20ensure%20Rs%20115%20crore%20in%20its%20banks%20as%20the%20lien%20marked%20in%20the%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20spend%20an%20amount%20over%20and%20above%20that.%20This%20means%20that%20Rs%20115%20crores%20have%20been%20frozen.%20This%20Rs%20115%20crores%20is%20much%20more%20than%20we%20have%20in%20our%20current%20accounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Democracy%20frozen%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Maken%20said%20that%20both%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Youth%20Congress%20have%20been%20frozen.%20He%20said%20it%20is%20democracy%20that%20has%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20been%20%E2%80%9Cfrozen%E2%80%9D%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDemocracy%20has%20completely%20ended%20in%20India.%20Day%20before%20yesterday%20we%20found%20out%20that%20the%20cheques%20we%20are%20issuing%20are%20not%20being%20honoured%20by%20banks.%20When%20we%20looked%20into%20this%20we%20were%20told%20that%20all%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20main%20opposition%20party%20have%20been%20frozen.%20The%20account%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20been%20locked.%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20have%20not%20been%20frozen%20but%20democracy%20has%20been%20frozen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaken%20pointed%20to%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20freeze.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20freezing%20the%20main%20opposition%20parties%20accounts%20two%20weeks%20before%20elections%20are%20announced%2C%20what%20is%20the%20government%20trying%20to%20prove%3F%20Not%20just%20the%20Congress%2C%20even%20Youth%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20have%20been%20frozen%20last%20evening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Pay%20Rs%20210%20crores%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Income%20Tax%20department%2C%20after%20freezing%20Youth%20Congress%20and%20Congress%20accounts%2C%20has%20asked%20for%20recovery%20of%20Rs%20210%20crores.%20This%20is%20not%20money%20from%20big%20businesses%20or%20corporate%20accounts%20or%20corporate%20bonds%20money.%20This%20is%20the%20money%20we%20collected%20from%20online%20crowdfunding%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maken%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Youth%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20money%20was%20collected%20through%20membership%20drives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20this%20money%20has%20been%20frozen%20by%20the%20government.%20Corporate%20bonds%20money%20which%20has%20been%20declared%20unconstitutional%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20now%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20they%20are%20spending%20it.%20How%20will%20democracy%20survive%20in%20India%3F%20Democracy%20has%20ended.%20If%20any%20political%20party%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20are%20frozen%20two%20weeks%20before%20elections%20are%20declared%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20more%20concerning.%20Will%20this%20be%20a%20one-party%20political%20system%3F%20No%20other%20party%20will%20have%20the%20right%20to%20survive%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Filed%20late%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20has%20said%20that%20their%20accounts%20have%20been%20frozen%20in%20connection%20with%20income%20tax%20returns%20being%20filed%20late%20in%20FY%202018-2019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20the%20accounts%20have%20been%20frozen%20and%20its%20timing%20cannot%20be%20more%20laughable.%20They%20have%20asked%20for%20Rs%20210%20crore%20in%20recovery%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20income%20tax%20returns%20filed%20in%20FY%202018-19.%20There%20are%20two%20reasons%2C%20that%20we%20were%20supposed%20to%20file%20returns%20by%20December%2031%2C%202019%20and%20maybe%20it%20was%20filed%2045%20days%20late.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20second%20reason%20is%20that%202018-19%20was%20an%20election%20year.%20And%20in%20that%20year%20Congress%20party%20had%20receipts%20of%20Rs%20199%20crores%20that%20was%20spent%20on%20elections.%20Of%20that%20Rs%2014%2C40%2C000%20was%20given%20in%20cash%20by%20our%20MPs%20and%20MLAs.%20And%20because%20this%20was%20given%20in%20cash%20we%20have%20been%20imposed%20a%20penalty%20of%20Rs%20210%20crore.%20Now%20after%20five%20years%2C%20just%20before%20elections%20are%20declared%20our%20accounts%20have%20been%20frozen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%20after%20electoral%20bond%20judgment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99%20claims%20come%20just%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20declared%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20as%20unconstitutional%20and%20asked%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20furnish%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20the%20details%20of%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20which%20would%20presumably%20include%20donors%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20details%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20which%20received%20the%20contributions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20was%20brought%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20early%20in%202018.%20Through%20it%2C%20companies%20and%20individuals%20in%20India%20can%20make%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20demanded%20that%20if%20any%20account%20should%20be%20frozen%20it%20should%20be%20that%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20%E2%80%9Creceived%20unconstitutional%20corporate%20bonds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20r%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-received-almost-90-of-all-corporate-donations-to-political-parties-in-2022-23%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eeport%20by%20election%20watchdog%20ADR%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%20in%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20nearly%2090%25%20of%20all%20corporate%20donations%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202022-23.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20statement%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20party%20would%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20to%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPower%20drunk%20Modi%20Govt%20has%20frozen%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20Opposition%20party%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20just%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20deep%20assault%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20Democracy%20!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UNCONSTITUTIONAL%20money%20collected%20by%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20utilised%20by%20them%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1758374494387990726%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20UNCONSTITUTIONAL%20money%20collected%20by%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20utilised%20by%20them%20for%20elections%2C%20but%20the%20money%20collected%20by%20us%20through%20CROWDFUNDING%20shall%20be%20sealed!%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20appeal%20to%20the%20Judiciary%20to%20save%20the%20multi-party%20system%20in%20this%20country%20and%20protect%20India%E2%80%99s%20Democracy.%20We%20will%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20and%20fight%20strongly%20against%20this%20autocracy%20!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708065054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16115257%2FUntitled-design-14.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-bank-accounts-frozen-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20said%20that%20the%20unconstitutional%20money%20collected%20by%20the%20BJP%20'would%20be%20utilised%20by%20them%20for%20elections%2C%20but%20the%20money%20collected%20by%20us%20%5BCongress%5D%20through%20crowdfunding%20shall%20be%20sealed.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-bank-accounts-frozen-election%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223rd%20Test%3A%20Why%20England%20started%20their%20innings%20at%205%2F0%20against%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708064699000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107744471%2Cimgsize-45754.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fengland-in-india%2F3rd-test-why-england-will-start-at-50-against-india%2Farticleshow%2F107744377.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20India%20vs%20England%20Test%20match%2C%20Indian%20batters%20were%20penalized%20for%20running%20on%20the%20pitch.%20Both%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20were%20fined%20according%20to%20MCC's%20law%2041.14.1.%20According%20to%20the%20laws%20of%20cricket%2C%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20or%20avoidable%20damage%20to%20the%20pitch%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20offence.%20Jadeja%20was%20warned%20for%20running%20on%20the%20pitch%20on%20the%20opening%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gramin%20Bharat%20Bandh%3A%20Prominent%20Citizens%20Urge%20Nation%20to%20Stand%20With%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16094243%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-9.40.40-AM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Almost%20300%20prominent%20citizens%20including%20journalists%2C%20scholars%2C%20activists%20and%20lawmakers%20have%20issued%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20nation%20to%20stand%20with%20its%20farmers%20and%20support%20their%20call%20for%20an%20all-India%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20has%20come%20as%20part%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20push%20for%20a%20guarantee%20of%20minimum%20support%20price%20and%20for%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20make%20good%20on%20its%20promises%20to%20them%2C%20when%20they%20withdrew%20their%20protest%20in%202021%20after%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20central%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20increasing%20distress%20among%20farmers%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20other%20marginalised%20people%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20trying%20to%20resurrect%20the%20discredited%20three%20farm%20laws%20through%20the%20backdoor%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20released%20by%20the%20prominent%20citizens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20signatories%20are%20journalist%20P.%20%3C%2Fspan%3ESainath%2C%20former%20bureaucrat%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%2C%20%3Cspan%3E%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%20national%20president%20Ashok%20Dhawale%2C%20Delhi%20Science%20Forum%E2%80%99s%20Dinesh%20Abrol%2C%20activist%20Lalita%20Ramdas%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Jawhar%20Sircar%2C%20historian%20Mridula%20Mukherjee%2C%20academic%20Arun%20Kumar%20and%20others.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20their%20plea%20to%20citizens%20is%20produced%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20levels%20of%20distress%20among%20farmers%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20other%20marginalised%20people%20are%20reaching%20new%20highs.%20The%20response%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20is%20to%20try%2C%20among%20other%20moves%2C%20resurrecting%20the%20discredited%20three%20farm%20laws%20via%20the%20backdoor.%20Meanwhile%2C%20far%20from%20doubling%20farmers%20income%20by%202022%20as%20this%20government%20promised%20it%20would%2C%20real%20incomes%20of%20agricultural%20households%20actually%20declined%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20whole%20promise%20of%20minimum%20support%20prices%20genuinely%20reflecting%20the%20comprehensive%20cost%20of%20production%20plus%2050%25%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20mockery.%20This%20despite%20the%20steep%20rise%20in%20input%20costs%20for%20cultivators.%20Correspondingly%2C%20corporates%20%E2%80%93%20which%20monopolise%20those%20inputs%20%E2%80%93%20are%20tightening%20their%20grip%20on%20Indian%20agriculture.%20Farm%20household%20debt%20is%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20and%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20farmer%20suicides%20is%20being%20reported%20from%20Marathwada%20and%20Vidarbha%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20elsewhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20country%20is%20yet%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20devastation%20of%20Covid-19%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20government%20is%20boasting%20how%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cshown%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%20the%20way%20ahead%20in%20handling%20it%2C%20and%20also%20moving%20forward%20post-pandemic.%20India%20witnessed%20the%20largest%20ever%20wave%20of%20human%20movement%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Creverse%20migrations%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20but%20there%20is%20no%20interest%20in%20strengthening%20the%20MGNREGS.%20Allocations%20are%20reducing%20and%20worsening%20the%20implementation%20process%20by%20linking%20it%20to%20Aadhar%20compliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20agricultural%20workers%2C%20a%20major%20component%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20agricultural%20population%2C%20are%20the%20worst-hit.%20Pushed%20into%20absolute%20poverty%20and%20destitution%2C%20they%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20migrate%20to%20towns%20and%20cities%20in%20big%20number%2C%20devoid%20of%20any%20social%20security.%20Real%20wages%20in%20rural%20India%20have%20actually%20fallen%20further%20since%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFood%20prices%20are%20soaring%20with%20inflation%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20country%20already%20ranking%20111%20out%20of%20125%20nations%20in%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index.%20The%20government%20is%20still%20not%20universalising%20%E2%80%9CPublic%20Distribution%20System%20(PDS)%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20using%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20ration%E2%80%9D%20to%20garner%20votes%20from%20the%20poor%20for%20the%20ruling%20party.%20The%20government%20is%20privatising%20school%20and%20college%20education.%20The%20New%20Education%20Policy%20does%20not%20guarantee%20%E2%80%9CRight%20to%20Free%20Education%E2%80%9D.%20Toilets%2C%20cooking%20gas%20cylinder%20and%20piped%20water%20do%20not%20amount%20to%20guaranteeing%20public%20health%20and%20sanitation%20for%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20mounting%20privatisation%20of%20public%20sector%20units%20and%20their%20consequent%20capture%20by%20corporations%20will%20bring%20further%20pressure%20on%20the%20common%20people.%20The%20workers%20are%20faced%20with%20rising%20unemployment%2C%20job%20losses%20and%20spiraling%20prices%20of%20all%20essentials.%20All%20their%20hard-won%20rights%20are%20being%20watered%20down%20through%20Labour%20Codes%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%9D.%20Permanent%20jobs%20are%20declining%20sharply.%20Government%20vacancies%20remain%20unfilled.%20Outsourcing%2C%20contract%20work%20in%20various%20formats%2C%20fixed%20term%20employment%3B%20gig%20work%20etc.%20along%20with%20drastic%20decline%20in%20real%20wage%20level%20on%20the%20whole%20is%20becoming%20the%20new%20normal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20actions%20of%20the%20Government%20at%20the%20Centre%20are%20against%20the%20federal%20structure%20of%20our%20nation.%20The%20national%20economy%20needs%20to%20be%20protected%20from%20the%20malice%20of%20the%20systemic%20crisis%20of%20the%20neoliberal%20policies.%20The%20government%20needs%20to%20secure%20employment%20to%20put%20more%20money%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20common%20people%20who%20create%20our%20national%20wealth%20and%20keep%20the%20national%20economy%20running.%20The%20government%20should%20ensure%20the%20implementation%20of%20statutory%20minimum%20wages%20and%20expand%20and%20universalize%20social%20security%20measures%2C%20particularly%20for%20women%20workers%20and%20informal%20labour%20from%20vulnerable%20social%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20needs%20to%20restore%20the%20role%20of%20the%20public%20sector%20and%20cooperatives%20in%20the%20distribution%20and%20supply%20of%20agricultural%20inputs.%20The%20government%20should%20strengthen%20the%20state-owned%20mandies%20and%20provide%20MSP%20for%20agricultural%20produce%20in%20all%20regions%20as%20per%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20recommendation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%5C%22%3EFarmers%E2%80%99%20Protest%3A%20Modi%20Government%20Used%20British-Era%20Law%20to%20Give%20Itself%20Powers%20to%20Suspend%20Internet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20should%20implement%20a%20comprehensive%20Loan%20Waiver%20Scheme%20to%20free%20all%20the%20farm%20households%20from%20the%20trap%20of%20indebtedness.%20It%20should%20waive%20the%20debts%20and%20provide%20support%20for%20women%20and%20families%20impacted%20by%20the%20rising%20suicides%20of%20farmers%20and%20agricultural%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStringent%20implementation%20of%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20(FRA)%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20priority%20and%20the%20provision%20of%20joint%20pattas%20should%20be%20respected%20while%20settling%20claims.%20The%20government%20should%20withdraw%20the%20Forest%20(Conservation)%20Act%2C%202023%20which%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eprovides%20for%20the%20de-reservation%20of%20reserved%20forests%2C%20use%20of%20forest%20land%20for%20non-forest%20purpose%2C%20assign%20forest%20land%20by%20way%20of%20lease%20or%20otherwise%20to%20private%20entities%20and%20clearing%20of%20naturally%20grown%20trees%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20reforestation%20and%20permits%20clearance%20of%20a%20forest%20without%20even%20informing%20the%20residents.%20The%20government%20should%20ensure%20land%20to%20the%20tiller%20and%20recognize%20the%20rights%20of%20women%20farmers%20and%20tenants.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20to%20common%20resources%20should%20be%20protected%20and%20strengthened.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20should%20make%20Right%20to%20Work%20a%20fundamental%20right.%20Fill%20sanctioned%20posts%20and%20generate%20employment%20for%20the%20unemployed.%20Expand%20and%20implement%20MGNREGS%20(200%20days%20per%20year%20and%20Rs.800%2F-per%20day%20wage)%2C%20and%20remove%20the%20mandatory%20provision%20of%20Aadhaar%20based%20payments%20for%20workers.%20The%20government%20should%20enact%20the%20Urban%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act.%20Withdraw%20the%20pro-corporate%20PM%20Fasal%20Bima%20Yojana%20and%20establish%20a%20comprehensive%20Public%20Sector%20Crop%20Insurance%20Scheme%20for%20all%20crops%2C%20to%20compensate%20farmers%20for%20losses%20due%20to%20climatic%20change%2C%20drought%2C%20flood%2C%20crop%20related%20diseases%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20demand%20from%20the%20government%20to%20budget%20for%20a%20country-wide%20programme%20of%20localized%20land%2Fsoil%20and%20water%20regeneration%20oriented%20at%20creating%20sustainable%20natural%20resource%20assets%20for%20strengthening%20of%20local%20economies%20to%20stop%20the%20corporate%20penetration%20into%20the%20sectors%20related%20to%20agriculture%20and%20rural%20industries%20space.%20The%20government%20should%20enhance%20public%20investment%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20cost%20of%20production.%20Integrated%20farming%20%2F%20low%20external%20input%20farming%20%2F%20natural%20farming%2C%20especially%20among%20small-marginal%20farmers%2C%20should%20receive%20adequate%20financial%20support%20and%20marketing%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20should%20increase%20and%20restore%20tax%20on%20corporates%20to%20at%20least%20the%20pre%202018%20level%20of%2030%25%20and%20the%20marginal%20tax%20on%20the%20rich%20and%20super-rich%20to%20a%20reasonable%20level%20of%20at%20least%2040%25.%20The%20government%20should%20restore%20Wealth%20Tax%20and%20Succession%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETax.%20We%20demand%20programmes%20and%20policy%20of%20re-establishing%20communal%20harmony%20among%20people%20of%20different%20faiths%2C%20languages%2C%20and%20cultures%2C%20and%20seek%20prompt%20action%20against%20those%20spreading%20hatred%20and%20enmity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Agenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWriters%2C%20intellectuals%2C%20journalists%2C%20social%20activists%20and%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20are%20being%20targeted%20on%20flimsy%20grounds%20only%20for%20criticizing%20this%20Government%20with%20the%20help%20of%20government%20agencies%20such%20as%20the%20ED%2C%20CBI%20and%20NIA%20and%20through%20misuse%20of%20nefarious%20laws%20such%20as%20UAPA%20and%20Sedition%20Act%20etc.%20This%20is%20aimed%20to%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20terror%2C%20to%20silence%20all%20opposition%20and%20dissent%2C%20and%20sabotage%20democratic%20processes.%20The%20entire%20system%20of%20governance%20that%20promotes%20and%20sustains%20the%20loot%20and%20plunder%20of%20the%20people%20as%20well%20as%20the%20national%20economy%20stands%20exposed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20demand%20from%20the%20government%20to%20repeal%20laws%20and%20provisions%20that%20enable%20stifling%20of%20democratic%20dissent%20or%20provide%20draconian%20power%20to%20the%20state%20apparatus.%20We%20demand%20mandatory%20environmental%20and%20social%20impact%20assessments%20of%20projects%2C%20programmes%2C%20schemes%20and%20sectors%2C%20through%20independent%20agencies.%20We%20demand%20the%20repeal%20of%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20curb%20academic%20freedom%20and%20create%20favourable%20conditions%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20scientific%20temper%20and%20humanism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20should%20gracefully%20accept%20the%20demands%20of%20Farmers%20and%20Workers%2C%20Women%2C%20Youth%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Minorities%20for%20which%20February%2016%20action%20has%20been%20announced.%20Through%20the%20Gramin%20Bharat%20Bandh%20and%20Strike%20called%20by%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20an