g%20point.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103142%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.28.50%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x438.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103142%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.28.50%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x438.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103142%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.28.50%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x128.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103142%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.28.50%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697435%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22359%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Love%20Storiyaan%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EAn%20Unsuitable%20Girl%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDirected%20by%20Hardik%20Mehta%2C%20who%20has%20shown%20a%20wild%20range%20of%20temperaments%20from%20his%20breakout%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAmdavad%20Ma%20Famous%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2015)%20to%20Netflix%20series%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDecoupled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2021)%2C%20this%20episode%20is%20an%20urban%20Bollywood%20rom-com%20setup.%20Aekta%2C%20a%2033-year-old%20writer%2Feditor%20based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20meets%20Ullekh%2C%20a%20journalist%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20old-fashioned%20online%20way%E2%80%94in%20the%20comments%20section%20of%20her%20lifestyle%20blog.%20The%20conflict%20arises%20when%20Aekta%E2%80%99s%20two%20daughters%20from%20her%20first%20marriage%20have%20to%20approve%20of%20their%20mother%E2%80%99s%20partner%20before%20they%20can%20take%20it%20forward.%20The%20way%20Mehta%20reconstructs%20it%20using%20actors%2C%20I%20could%20imagine%20Manav%20Kaul%20and%20Shefali%20Shah%20playing%20Ullekh%20and%20Aekta%20in%20a%20fictitious%20version%20of%20this%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20strongest%20bit%20of%20this%20episode%20is%20Aekta%20confessing%20to%20discovering%20her%20self-worth%20in%20her%20job%20as%20a%20writer%2Feditor%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98light%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20dark%2C%20lonely%20marriage.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20playfulness%20to%20the%20story%20which%20makes%20it%20ripe%20for%20a%20Bollywood%20adaptation.%20Mehta%20employs%20that%20in%20a%20reconstruction%20scene%2C%20like%20one%20of%20Aekta%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20showing%20her%20hostility%20to%20Ullekh%20in%20a%20sweet%2C%20savage%20manner.%20The%20story%20is%20all%20trumps%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccuteness%E2%80%9D%20of%20it%20is%20all%20that%20remains%20in%20the%20end%2C%20overcoming%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20stagey%20craft.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103131%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x457.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103131%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x457.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103131%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x134.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103131%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697434%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22375%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22w