Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20popularity%20and%20acceptance%20is%20over-hyped%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20%E2%80%9Cabsence%E2%80%9D%20of%20an%20all-India%20opposition%20figure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAlliance%20Calculus%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20ensure%20that%20the%20anti-BJP%20vote%20does%20get%20divided%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20garner%20all%20the%20anti-incumbency%20votes%20in%20states%20where%20non-BJP%20parties%20are%20in%20power%3B%20after%20all%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20the%20only%20party%20that%20has%20the%20experience%20of%20winning%20or%20losing%20elections.%20Political%20acumen%20and%20imagination%20are%20not%20the%20monopoly%20of%20the%20Modi-Shah%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejodi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20must%20follow%2C%20that%20an%20electoral%20alliance%20among%20all%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents%20is%20not%20an%20end%20itself%3B%20rather%2C%20the%20primary%20purpose%20of%20the%20alliance%20is%20to%20find%20the%20creativity%20and%20imagination%20at%20the%20local%2Fconstituency%20level%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20the%20BJP%20loses%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20seats.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Deng%20Xiaoping%20axiom%2C%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20which%20party%20wins%20as%20long%20as%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20get%20the%20seat.%C2%A0%20There%20cannot%20be%20any%20doubt%20as%20to%20who%20is%20the%20principal%20%E2%80%9Cenemy%E2%80%9D%20and%20his%20defeat%20has%20to%20be%20the%20one%20and%20only%20consideration.%C2%A0%20A%20brutal%20clarity%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20to%20be%20done%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20begin%20with%2C%20a%20joint%20statement%20of%20purpose%2C%20with%20a%20few%20specific%20promises%2C%20from%20all%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20and%20leaders%2C%20should%20kick-start%20the%20process.%20The%20idea%20should%20be%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20how%20the%20democratic%20forces%20differ%20from%20the%20Modi-led%20coalition%20of%20vested%20interests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20here%20are%20a%20few%20suggestions%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EPromise%20to%20respect%20the%20neutrality%20and%20professional%20ethos%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EUndertake%20to%20restore%20constitutional%20institutions%20to%20their%20vital%20selves%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EDeclare%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20hold%20a%20press%20conference%20every%20six%20months%3B%20and%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20attend%20parliament%20regularly%2C%20and%20answer%20questions%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EState%20clearly%20that%20the%20media%20will%20not%20be%20subjected%20to%20arm-twisting%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20misuse%20of%20federal%20agencies%20for%20political%20purposes%20would%20be%20stopped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EFederal%20principles%20and%20practices%20will%20be%20followed%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20cooperation%20and%20accommodation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20tool-kit%20and%20its%20contents%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBitterness%20and%20bad%20blood%20in%20the%20sharing%20of%20seats%20should%20be%20put%20behind%3B%20instead%2C%20national%20leaders%20should%20direct%20their%20district%20level%20party%20leaders%2Factivists%20to%20organise%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esammelans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20there%20could%20be%20an%20exchange%20of%20ideas%2C%20experiences%2C%20resources%20and%20insights%20on%20how%20not%20to%20allow%20the%20BJP%20(with%20or%20without%20acts%20of%20omission%20or%20commission%20by%20the%20EC%20)%20to%20manipulate%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20would%20be%20need%20to%20hold%20join%20training%20and%20orientation%20camps%2C%20where%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20list%20is%20diligently%20examined%3B%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20must%20be%20ensured%20that%20all%20genuine%20voters%20actually%20get%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise.%20There%20have%20been%20disquieting%20reports%20of%20how%20in%20BJP-ruled%20states%20Muslim%20voters%20are%20impeded%20on%20voting%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbove%20all%2C%20the%20alliance%20leaders%20would%20need%20to%20appreciate%20the%20indispensability%20of%20creating%20an%20image%20of%20a%20purposefully%20united%20democratic%20phalanx.%20While%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20hold%20joint%20rallies%20and%20press%20conferences%2C%20they%20must%20direct%20and%20inspire%20their%20district%2Fconstituency%20level%20cadres%20and%20activists%20to%20work%20together.%20An%20understanding%20among%20the%20top%20leaders%20does%20not%20necessarily%20and%20automatically%20produce%20synergy%20at%20the%20district%20level.%20This%20habit%20of%20pooling%20resources%2C%20energies%20and%20experiences%20at%20the%20local%20level%20needs%20to%20be%20assiduously%20attended%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20by%20acting%20in%20a%20joint%20and%20collective%20manner%20will%20the%20opposition%20parties%20be%20able%20to%20effectively%20demand%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20performs%20its%20job%20in%20a%20neutral%20and%20professional%20manner%2C%20and%20that%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20does%20not%20abandon%20its%20role%20as%20the%20highest%20forum%20of%20appeal%20for%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election.%20Far%20too%20much%20is%20at%20stake%20for%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarish%20Khare%20is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%20The%20Tribune.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708059121000%2C%22vis