3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20spoke%20to%20several%20reporters%20who%20had%20attended%20the%20press%20conference.%20They%20confirmed%20that%20the%20press%20conference%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Sanvad%E2%80%99%20room%2C%20a%20space%20dedicated%20for%20the%20police%20press%20conference.%20One%20among%20them%2C%20Shashi%20Sharma%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20channel%20%E2%80%9CDabang%20Khabre%E2%80%9D%20on%20YouTube%2C%20was%20among%20the%20attendees.%20His%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20like%20many%20other%20from%20the%20region%2C%20carried%20Rane%E2%80%99s%20speech%20as%20is.%20In%20no%20time%2C%20the%20video%20had%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaikh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20had%20put%20out%20a%20video%20on%20his%20channel%20questioning%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20allow%20Rane%20to%20address%20the%20press%20from%20their%20office.%20This%20video%2C%20he%20says%20had%20to%20soon%20be%20taken%20down%20after%20a%20call%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Csenior%20officer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20419px)%2085vw%2C%20419px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15161649%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-15-at-3.10.53-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22419%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15161649%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-15-at-3.10.53-PM.jpeg%20999w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15161649%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-15-at-3.10.53-PM-250x300.jpeg%20250w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15161649%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-15-at-3.10.53-PM-852x1024.jpeg%20852w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697339%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22503%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20video%20story%20that%20journalist%20Sabeer%20Shaikh%20had%20to%20take%20down%20after%20he%20was%20allegedly%20threatened%20by%20a%20senior%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewrote%20to%20police%20commissioner%20Madhukar%20Pandey%2C%20additional%20commissioner%20Shrikant%20Pathak%20and%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police%20(DCP)%20Avinash%20Ambure%20who%20had%20reportedly%20met%20Rane%20before%20his%20press%20briefing.%20None%20of%20the%20three%20officers%20responded%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20messages.%20Pathak%20wrote%20back%20saying%20he%20is%20on%20a%20leave%20and%20directed%20this%20reporter%20to%20DCP%20Prakash%20Gaikwad%2C%20who%20too%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond.%20The%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20they%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20after%20Rane%E2%80%99s%20press%20conference%2C%20a%20second%20round%20of%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20region.%20Young%20men%2C%20sporting%20saffron%20flags%20and%20chanting%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%2C%20ran%20amok%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20vandalising%20shops%20belonging%20to%20Muslims.%20Many%20Muslim%20youth%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20Rane%E2%80%99s%20access%20to%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20space%20important%3F%20Besides%20the%20most%20obvious%20fact%20that%20a%20legislative%20leader%20accessing%20the%20police%20space%20so%20blatantly%20shows%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20operate%20independently%2C%20Rane%E2%80%99s%20potential%20role%20in%20instigating%20violence%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20January%2023%20is%20in%20question%20here.%20Many%20citizens%20of%20Mira%20Road%20and%20several%20rights%20organisations%20have%20raised%20questions%20on%20his%20direct%20involvement%20in%20instigating%20the%20Hindu%20crowd%20against%20Muslims.%20He%20has%2C%20for%20long%2C%20been%20making%20provocative%20speeches%20and%20threatening%20the%20Muslim%20community%20of%20dire%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20at%20the%20press%20meet%20in%20Mira%20Road%2C%20Rane%20whipped%20up%20a%20frenzy%20by%20making%20baseless%20claims%20that%20Hindu%20women%20were%20%E2%80%9Cunsafe%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20city%2C%20that%20Mira%20Road%20has%20become%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmini-Pakistan%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20over%2035%20Hindu%20women%20have%20been%20forcibly%20converted%20to%20Islam.%20Not%20just%20that%2C%20threatening%20the%20police%20inspector%2C%20Rane%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20getting%20fed%20biryani%20by%20them%20(the%20Muslims).%20Don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20our%20party%20is%20in%20power.%20Will%20get%20you%20suspended%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20session.%20Then%20don%E2%80%99t%20come%20crying%20%5Bto%20me%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Rane%20has%20made%20several%20such%20public%20speeches%2C%20including%20the%20most%20recent%20ones%20at%20Pandharpur%20and%20Govandi%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20he%20openly%20asked%20Hindus%20to%20take%20law%20into%20their%20own%20hands%20and%20implied%20that%20he%20and%20his%20supporters%20will%20be%20protected%20by%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20over%20three%20weeks%20since%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Mira%20Road.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fpolice-didnt-stop-the-mob-shopkeepers-injured-recount-hindutva-violence-at-mumbais-mira-road%5C%22%3Ea%20detailed%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20incident%20in%20which%20victims%20and%20eyewitnesses%20of%20the%20violence%20spoke%20about%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20complicity%20in%20the%20attack.%20The%20police%20have%20since%20filed%20eight%20FIRs%20in%20the%20several%20attacks%20that%20occurred%20between%20January%2021%20and%2023.%20While%20four%20FIRs%20are%20registered%20by%20Muslims%20who%20were%20attacked%20in%20the%20violence%2C%20the%20other%20four%20name%20Muslims%20as%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clear%20pattern%20can%20be%20seen%20here.%20In%20cases%20in%20which%20Muslim%20men%20are%20accused%2C%20multiple%20arrests%20have%20been%20made.%20In%20cases%20where%20Muslim%20youth%20have%20suffered%20grievous%20hurt%20or%20damage%20to%20their%20property%2C%20the%20police%20have%20made%20no%20arrests%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Shahood%20Anwar%2C%20who%20is%20representing%20the%20Muslim%20youth%20arrested%20here%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20besides%20the%20two%20minor%20boys%20who%20were%20released%20by%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%2C%20no%20one%20has%20been%20released%20on%20bail%20yet.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20applied%20for%20bail%20for%20four%20men%20and%20it%20is%20scheduled%20for%20hearing%20before%20the%20Thane%20sessions%20court%20on%20February%2015%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anwar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Anwar%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20biased%20nature%20of%20investigation%20in%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20police%20only%20took%20a%20NC%20(non-cognisable%20crimes)%20and%20refused%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708047026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15162506%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-15-at-3.10.25-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmira-road-bjp-leader-gave-communal-speech-in-the-police-commissioners-office%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitesh%20Rane%E2%80%99s%20press%20conference%20was%20not%20for%20all.%20Only%20a%20select%20few%20journalists%2C%20with%20established%20pro-Hindutva%20credentials%2C%20were%20allowed%20for%20the%20conference.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmira-road-bjp-leader-gave-communal-speech-in-the-police-commissioners-office%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'It%20is%20a%20lie'%3A%20Trump%20prosecutor%20defends%20relationship%22%2C%22co