Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freport-to-office-thrice-a-week-hcl-technologies-asks-dfs-employees-124021501493_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freport-to-office-thrice-a-week-hcl-technologies-asks-dfs-employees-124021501493_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madeleine%20McCann%20suspect%20Christian%20B%20'was%20a%20loner%20but%20never%20acted%20suspiciously'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708012560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-christian-b-madeleine_6455729.png%3F20240215142636%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmadeleine-mccann-suspect-christian-b-was-a-loner-but-never-acted-suspiciously-13072317%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20prime%20suspect%20in%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Madeleine%20McCann%20will%20appear%20in%20court%20in%20Germany%20today%20accused%20of%20unrelated%20sex%20offences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmadeleine-mccann-suspect-christian-b-was-a-loner-but-never-acted-suspiciously-13072317%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmadeleine-mccann-suspect-christian-b-was-a-loner-but-never-acted-suspiciously-13072317%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmadeleine-mccann-suspect-christian-b-was-a-loner-but-never-acted-suspiciously-13072317%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme%20Violative%20of%20Voter%E2%80%99s%20Right%20to%20Information%3A%20Top%20Quotes%20From%20the%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20(February%2015)%20delivered%20its%20judgment%20on%20petitions%20contesting%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20ruling%20it%20as%20violative%20of%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20and%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20consisting%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20along%20with%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20JB%20Pardiwala%2C%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20delivered%20two%20separate%20but%20unanimous%20verdicts%20on%20the%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20scheme.%20Having%20reserved%20the%20verdict%20on%20November%202%2C%202023%2C%20the%20five-judge%20bench%20concluded%20the%20deliberations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20was%20introduced%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%202018%20and%20allowed%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%20Under%20this%20system%2C%20individuals%20or%20entities%20could%20purchase%20electoral%20bonds%20from%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20allocate%20them%20to%20a%20political%20party%20of%20their%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpart-of-secret-ballot-how-the-modi-govt-backed-electoral-bonds-in-the-supreme-court%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Part%20of%20Secret%20Ballot%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20the%20Modi%20Govt%20Backed%20Electoral%20Bonds%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20only%20the%20political%20parties%20registered%20under%20Section%2029A%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%20and%20which%20secured%20not%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20the%20votes%20polled%20in%20the%20last%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20a%20state%20legislative%20assembly%20are%20eligible%20to%20receive%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20bonds%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%20570%20crores%20have%20been%20sold%20in%20the%20latest%20phase%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20sale%20that%20lasted%20from%20January%202%20to%20January%2011%2C%202024%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Felectoral-bonds-worth-more-than-rs-570-crore-sold-in-january-alone-60-in-the-value-of-rs-1-crore%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20query%20filed%20by%20transparency%20activist%20Commodore%20Lokesh%20Batra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2F2793520172024-02-15-522601.pdf%5C%22%3Ekey%20quotes%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20on%20electoral%20bonds%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20and%20the%20impugned%20provisions%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20infringe%20upon%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20the%20voter%20by%20anonymising%20contribution%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20are%20violative%20of%20Article%2019%20(1)(a)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20CJI%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2F2793520172024-02-15-522601.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEconomic%20inequality%20leads%20to%20differing%20levels%20of%20political%20engagement%20because%20of%20the%20deep%20association%20between%20money%20and%20politics.%20At%20a%20primary%20level%2C%20political%20contributions%20give%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseat%20at%20the%20table%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20contributor.%20That%20is%2C%20it%20enhances%20access%20to%20legislators.%20This%20access%20also%20translates%20into%20influence%20over%20policymaking.%20An%20economically%20affluent%20person%20has%20a%20higher%20ability%20to%20make%20financial%20contributions%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20legitimate%20possibility%20that%20financial%20contribution%20to%20a%20political%20party%20would%20lead%20to%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements%20because%20of%20the%20close%20nexus%20between%20money%20and%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInformation%20about%20political%20funding%20would%20enable%20a%20voter%20to%20assess%20if%20there%20is%20a%20correlation%20between%20policymaking%20and%20financial%20contributions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-are-illegal-now-but-who-benefited-for-the-6-years-they-lasted%5C%22%3EElectoral%20Bonds%20Are%20Illegal%20Now.%20But%20Who%20Benefitted%20for%20the%206%2B%20Years%20They%20Lasted%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ability%20of%20a%20company%20to%20influence%20the%20electoral%20process%20through%20political%20contributions%20is%20much%20higher%20when%20compared%20to%20that%20of%20an%20individual.%20A%20company%20has%20a%20much%20graver%20influence%20on%20the%20political%20process%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20quantum%20of%20money%20contributed%20to%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20purpose%20of%20making%20such%20contributions.%20Contributions%20made%20by%20individuals%20have%20a%20degree%20of%20support%20or%20affiliation%20to%20a%20political%20association.%20However%2C%20contributions%20made%20by%20companies%20are%20purely%20business%20transactions%2C%20made%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20securing%20benefits%20in%20return.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20Section%20182%20is%20to%20curb%20corruption%20in%20electoral%20financing.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20banning%20a%20government%20company%20from%20contributing%20is%20to%20prevent%20such%20companies%20from%20entering%20into%20the%20political%20fray%20by%20making%20contributions%20to%20political%20parties.%20The%20amendment%20to%20Section%20182%20by%20permitting%20unlimited%20corporate%20contributions%20(including%20by%20shell%20companies)%20authorizes%20unrestrained%20influence%20of%20companies%20on%20the%20electoral%20process.%20This%20is%20violative%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20and%20political%20equality%20captured%20in%20the%20value%20of%20%E2%80%9Cone%20person%20one%20vote%E2%80%9D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708011396000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felectoral-bonds-top-supreme-court-quotes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Information%20about%20political%20funding%20would%20enable%20a%20voter%20to%20assess%20if%20there%20is%20a%20correlation%20between%20policymaking%20and%20financial%20contributions%2C'%20said%20the%20top%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felectoral-bonds-top-supreme-court-quotes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%20at%20Shambhu%20Barrier%20Vow%20Not%20to%20Return%20Until%20Centre%20Enacts%20a%20Law%20on%20MSP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15202856%2Fimage-1831.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatiala%20(Shambhu%20Barrier%2C%20Punjab)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Tractor-trollies%20have%20queued%20up%20for%20as%20long%20as%20seven-eight%20kilometres%20at%20Shambhu%20barrier%20on%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%20as%20farmers%20are%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20relent%20in%20their%20march%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20has%20swelled%20manifold%20since%20visuals%20spread%20across%20the%20media%20showing%20security%20forces%20using%20tear%20gas%20and%20other%20excessive%20force%20to%20halt%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fas-farmers-head-to-delhi-for-protest-haryana-govt-creates-hurdles-on-their-path%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Chalo%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20began%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scene%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20is%20an%20exact%20replay%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20in%202020%20outside%20Delhi%20borders.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20the%20farmers%20are%20midway%20through%20their%20journey.%20They%20say%20they%20are%20even%20more%20determined%20to%20confront%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaspal%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Amritsar%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20last%20time%2C%20while%20calling%20off%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20they%20made%20a%20mistake%20by%20believing%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20verbal%20assurances%20on%20enacting%20a%20law%20on%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20as%20well%20as%20other%20demands%20on%20compensation%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20repeat%20this%20mistake%20this%20time.%20We%20will%20not%20return%20home%20until%20the%20Centre%20enacts%20a%20law%20and%20fulfils%20other%20demands%2C%20whether%20it%20takes%20us%2013%20days%2C%2013%20months%20or%2013%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20farmer%20Baltej%20Singh%20from%20Ferozepur%20explained%20why%20a%20guarantee%20on%20the%20MSP%20law%20is%20important%2C%20not%20just%20for%20them%2C%20but%20for%20farmers%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20wheat-paddy%20crop%20cycle%20has%20fully%20destroyed%20Punjab%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Punjab%20is%20not%20even%20a%20rice%20consumer.%20There%20are%20places%20where%20the%20water%20level%20has%20tanked%20to%20a%20bare%20minimum%20due%20to%20farmers%E2%80%99%20economic%20dependence%20on%20the%20wheat-paddy%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20happening%20because%20of%20the%20faulty%20MSP%20system%20in%20place.%20The%20Centre%20sets%20MSP%20for%2023%20crops%2C%20yet%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20to%20ensure%20that%20crops%20other%20than%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20are%20procured%20at%20the%20government-announced%20MSP.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%2020%20acres%20of%20farmland.%20If%20I%20decide%20to%20shun%20the%20paddy%20crop%20and%20sow%20maize%20or%20pulses%2C%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee%20if%20I%E2%80%99ll%20get%20MSP%20for%20my%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%20farmers%20still%20receive%20an%20MSP%20on%20wheat%20and%20paddy%2C%20Baltej%20said.%20However%2C%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20other%20states%2C%20farmers%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20receive%20MSP%20on%20these%20crops%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20saying%20that%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20purchase%20all%20the%20crops%20under%20the%20MSP%20regime.%20However%2C%20it%20can%20at%20least%20bring%20a%20law%20which%20ensures%20that%20the%20MSP%20announced%20on%20crops%20will%20not%20be%20purchased%20below%20government%20rates%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20procured%20by%20the%20government%20or%20private%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203146%2Fimage-1833.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22957%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203146%2Fimage-1833.png%20957w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203146%2Fimage-1833-300x198.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EProtesters%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border.%20Photo%3A%20Vivek%20Gupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarsem%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Gurdaspur%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20it%20is%20a%20now%20or%20never%20situation%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20here%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%20We%20know%20that%20Modi%20is%20deliberately%20stopping%20us%20from%20reaching%20Delhi%2C%20fearing%20a%20dent%20in%20his%20popularity%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20But%20this%20is%20his%20doing.%20When%20he%20had%20assured%20us%20of%20a%20law%20on%20MSP%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20last%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202021%2C%20why%20did%20his%20government%20sit%20over%20it%20for%20close%20to%20three%20years%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20farmer%2C%20Avtar%20Singh%2C%20said%20it%20is%20not%20just%20a%20question%20of%20law%20on%20MSP%3B%20crop%20pricing%20is%20also%20not%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20thereby%20rendering%20farming%20unprofitable%20and%20leaving%20farmers%20in%20debt.%20%E2%80%9CGiving%20Rs%206%2C000%20cash%20subsidy%20to%20farmers%20is%20a%20joke.%20We%20want%20the%20right%20value%20for%20our%20crop%2C%20not%20less%20than%20the%20government-announced%20MSP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESituation%20calm%20but%20temporarily%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%2C%20farmers%20have%20camped%20on%20the%20road%20with%20%3Cem%3Elangars%3C%2Fem%3E%20(free%20meals)%20being%20served%20all%20around%20the%20clock%20to%20feed%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203015%2Fimage-1832.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22956%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203015%2Fimage-1832.png%20956w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203015%2Fimage-1832-300x200.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22637%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EProtesters%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border.%20Photo%3A%20Vivek%20Gupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurpeet%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Batala%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20even%20as%20farmers%20were%20marching%20peacefully%2C%20security%20forces%20standing%20on%20the%20Haryana%20side%20of%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20used%20excessive%20force%2C%20injuring%20several%20of%20their%20fellow%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CWas%20it%20justified%20to%20use%20brutal%20force%20in%20response%20to%20our%20legitimate%20demands%3F%20The%20Modi%20government%20is%20certainly%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20its%20arrogance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20despite%20police%20brutality%2C%20the%20protesters%20managed%20to%20break%20through%20their%20initial%20line%20of%20defence.%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20calm%20as%20we%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20next%20line%20of%20action%20from%20our%20leaders.%20Once%20we%20get%20a%20go-ahead%2C%20we%20will%20definitely%20march%20ahead%20to%20Delhi%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20it%20takes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20noticeable%20trend%20at%20the%20protest%20site%20is%20the%20significant%20presence%20of%20youngsters%2C%20who%20are%20leading%20the%20march.%20The%20crowd%20is%20swelling%20by%20the%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20is%20led%20by%20a%20faction%20group%20of%20the%20Sanyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%2C%20which%20played%20a%20decisive%20role%20in%20the%202020%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20(KMSC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Ffarmers-protest-panel-of-3-union-ministers-to-hold-talks-with-farmer-leaders-in-chandigarh%2Farticleshow%2F107706361.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethird%20round%20of%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%20betwe